\id JDG - Aruamu NT - drafted by Pais Asefi; exeg checked by Marsha Miles, Robin Namai and Pais Asefi March 2016; Comprehension checked by Francis Dagonov and team May 2016; Consultant checked by Wes Beasley and Martin, Simon, Lawrence, Michael in August 2016.
\h Gumazir Dapaniba
\toc3 GD
\toc2 Gumazir Dapaniba
\toc1 Israelian Gumazir Dapaniba
\mt1 Israelian Gumazir Dapaniba
\mt2 O
\mt1 Jasba
\imt1 Akar faragha zuim
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam, an eghaghanir av…®riba iti. Eghaghanir kaba, da Israelia Kenan…®n nguazim inigha a gapiazir dughiam…®n ikegha ghua me uari baghav…®ra atrivim inizir dughiam…®n oto. A Israelian gumazir dapanir mabar ik…®r…®m…®rim ko me amizir ingangarir mabagh eghari. Gumazir dapanir kabar av…®riba, me kotiaba baragha akaba ak…®rir arazibagh fozir puvat…®. Puvat…®. Me m…®dorozibar faragha zuir gumaziba. Apaniba Israelia gas…®ghasigh os…®mt…®ziba me dar…®ghasava amima God Israelian akurvaghasa me am…®sefe. Men ziabar kara: Otniel, Ehut, Samgar, Debora, Barak, Gideon, Abimelek, Tola, Jair, Jepta, Elon, Apdon ko Samson.
\ip Ak…®nafarir kam…®n God bizir ekiar mam…®n en sure damuasa, a kamak…®n. Israelia bar deraghv…®ra God…®n akabar g…®n mang…®va, egh deraghv…®ra ikiam. Me an akaba baraghan kogh, egh me ikuvigham. Ez…® tuavir igharazir mam kam gafira. Me God…®n akaba baraghan kogh os…®mt…®zim init…®, God men apangkuvigh ua men akurvagham. Me navibagh iragh arazir kuraba ateght…®, God uam men akurvagham. Ak…®nafarir kam…®n eghaghanir av…®riba, da tuavir igharazir kam azenara aneka. God uab…®, God…®n Araziba (o Diuteronomi) sapta 28…®n aven, tuavir kam isa gumazamizibar aka.
\c 1
\ms1 Gumazir dapaniba Israelia gatifa
\mr (Sapta 1--3)
\s1 Judan anabam ko Simeon…®n anabam…®n adarasi, atrivim Adoni Besek…®n suira
\p 
\v 1 Josua aremegha g…®vaz…®, Israelia kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azara, ‚ÄúTe m…®dorozim…®n faragh mang…® Kenania m…®sogham?‚Äù
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa kamagh…®n fogh, k…® nguazir kam isa Judan anabam…®n gumazamizibagh an…®ngi, kamagh…®n me ian faragh mangam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Judan anabam…®n adarazi kamagh…®n Simeon…®n anabam…®n adaraziv gei, ‚ÄúAveghbuaba, ia iz…® en g…®n mang…® nguazir God e dan…®ngasa m…®kemezim…®n mang…®va bar uari akuvagh, Kenanian adarazi ko m…®sogham. Egh g…®n e bar mogh…®ra mang…® nguazir God ia gan…®ngizim…®n mangam.‚Äù Ez…® Simeon…®n adarasi, Judan adarazi ko zui.
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Judan anabam…®n gumaziba m…®dorozim…®n faragha zuima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Kenania ko Peresia isa Judabagh an…®ngiz…®, me Besek…®n nguibar ekiam…®n 10,000plan gumazibav sogha, me ab…®ni.
\v 5 Me Adoni Besek ko an adarasi, Besek…®n nguibam…®n me batogha me m…®soke. Egha me bar Kenania ko Peresia ab…®ni.
\v 6 Ez…® Adoni Besek uab…® arima, Judaba an ag…®nt…®gha ghua an suira. Egha me an dafarir puzir amebamning aghorava an dagarir puzir amebamning sara dutu.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Adoni Besek kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fom…®ra atrivir 70plan dafarir puzir amebaba ko suer puziba aghorez…®ma, me dagher daghatevir muziarir nan dakozim…®n apengan iriba isa da api. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® me gamizir arazimra, God a ikaragha an na gami.‚Äù Ez…® Judaba Adoni Besek inigha ghua Jerusalem…®n ikia ghuav iti an areme.
\s1 Judan anabam…®n adarazi Jerusalem ko Hebron ini
\p 
\v 8 Judaba Jerusalem…®n gumaziba ko m…®sogha men nguazim ini. Egha men gumazibav sozi me ariaghirez…®, me men nguibam gaboroz…®, a isi.
\v 9 Me g…®n ghua, gumazamizir Kenanian m…®ghs…®ar dozibar itiba, ko Negev…®n Distrigh…®n itiba, ko saut…®n amadaghan nguazir vorogh…®ra zuim…®n itibav soghasa zui.
\v 10 Egha me g…®n ua ghua, Kenanian Hebron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itibav sosi, kar me fom…®ra kamagh…®n d…®borir nguibar ekiam, Kiriat Arba. Judaba uaghan Sesain adarazi ko Ahiman ko Talmain adarazi ab…®ni.
\s1 Otniel Debir…®n nguibar ekiam ini
\r (Josua 15:15-19)
\p 
\v 11 Egha Judaba nguibar kam ategha ghua Debir…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamizibav sosi. (Nguibar kam…®n ziar mam, Kiriat Sefer.)
\v 12 Ez…® Kalep kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazim Kiriat Sefer…®n gumazibav sogh me ab…®raght…®, k…® uan guivim Aksa a danight…® an an ikiam.‚Äù
\v 13 Ez…® Kalep…®n dozim Kenas, an otarim Otniel, nguibar kam…®n gumazibav sogha me ab…®ra. Ez…® Kalep uan guivim Aksa isa, a gan…®ngiz…® an an iti.
\p 
\v 14 Egha aning uaning…®n ikiava, Aksa Otniel bagha iza aneb…®rava, a m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® nan afeziam Kalep…®n azaraght…® a nguazitam atugh ga dan…®ngigh. Egha Aksa ghua Kalep batogha uan donkin faghaf…®ragha izaghirima, Kalep an azara, ‚ÄúK…® bizir tizitam n…® bagh a damuam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Aksa uan afeziam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® bizir aghuitam na dan…®ngigh. N…® faragha d…®paba puvat…®zir nguazim Negev…®n itir nguazir akuar mam abigha na gan…®ngi. Dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® d…®par em…®m…®riba itir nguazir aghuitam abigh na dan…®ngigh.‚Äù Ez…® Kalep d…®par em…®m…®riba itir nguazir pumuning a gan…®ngi. Aning Hebron…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n iti, mam p…®n amadaghan itima, mam v…®n amadaghan iti.
\s1 Judan anabam…®n adarazi ko Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi m…®dorozim gafira
\p 
\v 16 Moses…®n amerer afeziam, a Kin…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazir mam. Ez…® Moses…®n amerer afeziam…®n adarazi ko Judan anabam…®n adarasi, me Temer Detba itir nguibar ekiam, ategha ghua saut…®n amadaghan, Judan gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n, Negev…®n danganim…®n aven itir nguibar ekiam, Arat…®n borogh…®n ghue. Me ghua Amalekia ko danganir kam…®n iti.
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Judan anabam…®n gumaziba ko Simeon…®n anabam…®n gumaziba ghua, Kenanian Sefat…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itiba ko m…®sogha bar me ab…®ragha, bar nguibar kam ag…®fa. Kamagh…®n, me ziar igiam, ‚ÄúHorma,‚Äù a gat…®.
\v 18 Me uaghan Gasan nguibar ekiam ko Askelon…®n nguibar ekiam ko Ekron…®n nguibar ekiam ko nguazir dar borogh…®n itiba sara ini.
\p 
\v 19 Ikiav…®ra Itir God Judabar akuraz…®, me m…®ghs…®ar dozibar itir nguaziba ini. Ez…® ongarim…®n borogh…®n nguazir vorogh…®ra itim…®n adarasi, me ain…®n karisba iti, kamagh…®n Judaba me batoghan ibura.
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Josua 15:13-14\x*Moses fom…®ra m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, me Hebron…®n nguibar ekiam isa Kalep gan…®ngi. Ez…® Kalep zuima, Anak…®n ovavir borir 3plan adarasi, Hebron…®n itima a me batoke.\f + \fr 1:20 \ft Ik…®zir kabar ziaba ves 10…®n iti, n…® D…®boboniba 13:22 uaghan an gan.\f*
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt Josua 15:63; 2 Samuel 5:6; 1 Eghaghaniba 11:4\x*Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarasi, me Jebusian Jerusalem…®n iti darazi batoghezir puvat…®, kamagh…®n Jebusia Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ikiav…®ra iti.
\s1 Josep…®n anabam…®n adarasi, Betel…®n nguibar ekiam ini
\p 
\v 22-23 Josep…®n anabam…®n adarazi uaghan kamagh…®ram ami. Me uaghan Betel…®n iti darazi ko m…®sosi. Me fom…®ra kamagh…®n nguibar ekiar kam d…®bori, Lus. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God me ko ikia men akura. Josep…®n anabam…®n adarasi, gumazir maba amadaz…®, me ghua nguibar ekiar kam mogomem…®n a getiagha rui.
\v 24 Gumazir kaba gumazir mam…®n gari, a nguibar ekiar mam ategha azenan zuima, me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tuavir ghua nguibar ekiam…®n aven zuim…®n gun e m…®kemeght…®ma, e paz…® n…® damighan kogham.‚Äù
\v 25 Ez…® a tuavir aven zuim men aka. Ez…® me aven ghua uan m…®dorozir sababar nguibar ekiar kam…®n aven itir gumazamiziba bar me m…®suaghar…®ki. Egha me gumazir kam ko an adaraziv soghezir puvat…®gha me ataghiz…®, me zui.
\v 26 Ez…® gumazir kam ghua Hitian nguazim…®n ghugha, nguibar ekiar mam…®n ingarigha kamagh a d…®bori, Lus. Ez…® ziar kam dat…®r…®gh…®n an ikiav…®ra iti.
\s1 Israelia igharaz darazir gumazamiziba bar me batoghezir puvat…®
\p 
\v 27 \x - \xo 1:27-28 \xt Josua 17:11-13\x*Ez…® Manasen anabam…®n adarasi, me Betsan nguibam…®n itir gumazamiziba, ko Tanak, Dor, Ipleam, Megido koma nguibar ekiar kabar borogh…®n itir nguibar doziba, me dar gumazamiziba batoghezir puvat…®.
\v 28 Ez…® g…®n Israelia ikia ghua gavgavigha, Kenanian gumazamizir kabagh amiz…®, me men ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar otifi. Israelia bar me batoghezir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 29 \x - \xo 1:29 \xt Josua 16:10\x*Efraim…®n anabam…®n gumaziba Kenan…®n gumazamizir Geser…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itiba batoghezir puvat…®, kamagh amiz…®, Kenanian gumazamizir kaba men tong…®n danganir kam…®n iti.
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® Sebulun…®n anabam…®n gumaziba, gumazamizir Kitron…®n nguibar ekiam ko Nahalal…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itiba batoghezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, Kenanian gumazamizir kaba men tong…®n ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® Sebulun…®n gumazamiziba, Kenania gamiz…®, me men ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar otifi.
\p 
\v 31 Ez…® Aser…®n anabam…®n gumaziba, gumazamizir Akon nguibar ekiam ko Saidon…®n nguibar ekiam ko Alap, Aksip, Helba, Afek ko Rehop…®n nguibar ekiabar itiba, me batoghezir puvat…®.
\v 32 Me, me batoghezir puvat…®, kamagh…®n, Aserian gumazamiziba Kenanian tong…®n ikiav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 33 Ez…® Naptalin anabam…®n gumaziba, gumazamizir Betsemes…®n nguibar ekiam ko Betanat…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itiba batoghezir puvat…®. Egha me Kenanian tong…®n iti. Egha Naptalin anabam…®n adarazigh amiz…®, me men ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar otifi.
\p 
\v 34 Ez…® Amoria gavgavigha Dan…®n anabam…®n gumazamiziba batoghez…®, me ghua m…®ghs…®ar danganim…®n ghue. Amoria me ataghiz…® me izaghira danganir zarim…®n itir puvat…®.
\v 35-36 Amoria uarira Heres…®n M…®ghs…®am ko, Aijalon…®n nguibar ekiam, ko Salbim…®n nguibar ekiam gapia. Ez…® men nguazir m…®taghniam, Tuighakabar M…®ghs…®am…®n P…®n Zuir Tuavim…®n ikegha ghua, Selan nguibam…®n otogha bar s…®vagha ghu. Ez…® dughiar maba, Josep…®n anabam…®n gumazamiziba me gativagha me gamiz…®, me men ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar otifi.
\c 2
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel Israelia m…®gei
\r (Josua 24:29-31)
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel, Gilgal…®n nguibam ategha, Bokim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. Egha kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® Isip…®n kantrin aven ia inigha iza, nguazir ian inazir afeziabar an…®ngasa akam ak…®rizim bagha zui. Egha k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄòAkar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir k…® ia koma amizim, k…® anebighan kogham.
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:12-13; God…®n Araziba 7:2-5\x*Kamagh…®n, ia gumazamizir nguazir kam…®n itiba ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavir tam damuan mark…®, k…® ian anogoroke. Ia men ofa gamir dakozibagh as…®ghas…®kigh.‚Äô K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n garima, ia nan Akar Gavgavim barazi puvat…®. Ia manmaghsua, arazir bar igharazim gami.
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:12; God…®n Araziba 7:16; Josua 23:13; Onger Akaba 106:36\x*Kamagh…®n, k…® kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, ia men nguazibar aven mang…® me batoghs…® damuamin dughiam…®n, k…® ian faragh mang…®ghan kogham. Puvat…®. Gumazir kaba ian apanibar otivigh azuazibar m…®n ian suigh ia damut…® ia ir…®, egh tuavir vorogh…®ra itim ategham. Eght…® men aseba bar puv…®ra ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba basamam, da gavgaviz o.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel, Israelia m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, me akar kaba baregha, bar puv…®ram azi.
\v 5 Kamagh…®n, me danganir kam kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúBokim.‚Äù Egha danganir kam…®n, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofa gami.\f + \fr 2:5 \ft Ziar kam Bokim, an m…®ngarim Hibrun akam…®n kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúAzi darasi.‚Äù\f*
\s1 Josua areme
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Josua Israelia amadaz…®, me ghua danganir God vaghvagha me bagha m…®sevegha me gan…®ngiziba inigha, dagh apia.
\v 7 Josua angam…®ra itir dughiam…®n, Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe. Egha Josua aremezir dughiam…®n g…®n, me uaghan an ziam fav…®ra iti. Me kamagh…®ram amua ghua, gumazir aruaba uan damazibar Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelia bagha amizir bizibar ganizir dughiam…®n tu.
\v 8 Nun…®n otarim Josua, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim, a 110plan azenibar ikegha areme.
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Josua 19:49-50\x*Ez…® me an kuam isa Timnat Heres…®n nguibar ekiam…®n anefa. Kar an nguazir otevir mamra, a Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar tong…®n ikia, not…®n amadaghan Gas…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n iti.
\v 10 Ez…® Josua ko otiviz…® darazi bar ariaghire, ez…® gumazamizir igiaba otivigha, men danganiba ini. Gumazamizir g…®n otivizir kabanang, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®fozir puvat…®. Egha bizir a Israelian akurvagha amiziba, bar da g…®n amada.
\s1 Israelia ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fer puvat…®
\p 
\v 11 Egha Israelia aser Balbar ziaba fava, arazir bar kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami.
\v 12 Me ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe puvat…®, a men inazir afeziabar God, a God…®n Isip…®n kantrin aven me inigha azenan izezim. Me d…®kavigha tintinibar gumazamizir men tong…®n itibar asebar ziaba fe. Israelia uan iteviba ap…®ra aser kabar ziaba fava, Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamima a bar men an…®ngaghe.
\v 13 Me ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n aghuagha an ategha, Bal…®n asem ko Astarten aser amizibar ziaba fe.
\p 
\v 14 \x - \xo 2:14 \xt Josua 7:12; 2 Atriviba 17:20; Onger Akaba 44:12; Aisaia 50:1\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar men an…®ngaghegha, m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ok…®mak…®ar gumaziba ataghiz…® me iza Israelia m…®sogha men biziba bar da okeme. Ikiav…®ra Itir God me isa apanibar agharim gat…®z…®, me tintinibar ikegha iza bar me ab…®ra. Israelia m…®tivigh gavgavigh uari bagh m…®soghan ibura.
\v 15 Me zurara m…®soghasa zuir dughiabar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God men apanim gamua men akurvazir puvat…®, ez…® me bar dughiar kuram…®n iti.
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God gumazir dapanir gavgavir maba isa Israelia gan…®ngi. Ez…® gumazir dapanir kaba, Israelian akuragha m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ok…®mak…®ar gumazibar aghariba da uam me ini.
\v 17 Ez…® gumazamiziba kamagh…®ram ami. Me gumazir dapaniba barazir puvat…®. Me ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasaragha mati tuavim…®n amizim tintinim…®n gumaziba bagha arui mogh…®n, me aseba bagha bar ikuvigha men damazibar uan teviba ap…®ri. Me fo, men inazir afeziaba fom…®ra God…®n Akar Gavgavibar g…®n zui, ez…® merara dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n amir puvat…®. Me zuam…®ra tuavir aghuir kam ataki.
\v 18 Dughiar av…®riba, apaniba paza Israelia gamima, me uan os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zazir me isir kaba bagha aziava arai. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God men apangkufi. Dughiaba zurara, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian ganasa gumazir dapaniba m…®sefi, egha a gumazir dapaniba vaghavagha me ko ikia men akurvasi. Ez…® gumazir dapanir kaba vaghvagha Israelian akurvagha apanibar gavgaviba da ua me isi. God zurara gumazir dapanir kam…®n akurvagh an gan mang…® an aremeghamin dughiam…®n tugham.
\v 19 Gumazir dapanir kam aremeghamin dughiam…®n g…®n, gumazamiziba uamategh uan arazir ghuribar amuam. Men arazir kuraba, men faragha ghuezir darazir arazir kurabagh afiragham. Me asebar g…®nt…®gha dar ziaba fa uan teviba ap…®ri. Me bar uan arazir kurar kaba ko akam batozir arazibar g…®n mangasa bar gavgafi, egha da atagh…®raghan aghua.
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar Israelian an…®ngaghegha, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumazamizir kaba, k…® fom…®ra men inazir afeziaba ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gamigha, an g…®n mangasa me m…®keme, ez…® me aneb…®ki. Me nan akam…®n g…®n zuir puvat…®.
\v 21 Josua angam…®ra itir dughiam…®n, a men nguaziba inizir puvat…®gha areme, kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® ik…®zir igharaziba batueghan kogham.
\v 22 K…® ik…®zir igharazir kabar amight…®, me Israelian n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba basamt…® k…® ganasa, me nan m…®g…®r…®g…®abar tuavim…®n g…®n mangam, mati men inazir afeziaba amiz…® mogh…®n, o puvat…®gham.‚Äù
\v 23 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ik…®zir igharazir kaba ataghiz…®, me Israelian nguazim…®n iti. A fom…®ra Josua ataghiz…®, a me m…®sogha me ab…®razir puvat…®. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God uaghan zuam…®ra me batueghan kogham.
\c 3
\s1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®dorozir arazibar Israelian akakaghasa
\p 
\v 1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God ik…®zir igharazir maba ataghiz…®ma, me Israelian tong…®n Kenan…®n nguazim…®n iti. Israelia faragha m…®sogha Kenan…®n nguazim ini, ez…® men marazi, m…®dorozir tam…®n ikezir puvat…®gha m…®dorozir arazibagh fozir puvat…®. God dat…®r…®gh…®n men gavgavim…®n ganigh foghasa.
\v 2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n damuva, vaghvagh Israelian igiar g…®n otiviziba m…®dorozim…®n me geghan men sure damuam.
\v 3 Kar God Kenan…®n nguazim…®n ataghizir ik…®ziba: Filistian 5plan nguibar ekiabar gumazamiziba, ko Kenan…®n nguibar ekiaba bar mogh…®ra, ko Saidon…®n gumazamiziba. Ez…® Hivian Lebanon…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n p…®n itiba, me Balhermon…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n ikegha ghua, Hamat…®n nguibam…®n zuir tuavir akam…®n tu.
\v 4 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelia tuis…®ghasa ifonge, me ti an Akar Gavgavibar g…®nt…®gham, o ti puvat…®gham? Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a gumazamizir kaba ataghiz…®ma, me Kenan…®n nguazim…®n iti. Akar Gavgavir kabanang, God fom…®ra men inazir afeziaba bagha Moses gan…®ngi.
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelia, me Kenanian tong…®n apia, me Hitia ko Amoria ko, Peresia ko, Hivia ko Jebusian gumazamiziba.
\v 6 Egha Israelia, Kenanian guiviba isa men iti, egha uan guiviba isa Kenanian otaribagh an…®di. Egha me men asebar ziaba fe.
\s1 Otniel gumazir dapanim…®n oto
\p 
\v 7 Egha Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kuram gami. Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan God, bak…®n…®gh…®nigha, arazir kuram gamigha Bal…®n aseba, ko Astarten aser amizibar ziaba fe.
\v 8 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian atara Mesopotemian atrivim Kusan Risataim ataghiz…®ma, a m…®dorozim…®n me gafira. Israelia 8plan azenibar atrivim Kusan Risataim…®n gavgavim…®n apengan iti.
\v 9 Egha Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha araima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me bagh akurvazir gumazir mam am…®sefe, an ziam Otniel. Otniel a Kenas…®n otarim, ez…® Kenas a Kalep…®n dozim. Ez…® Otniel atrivir kam da ua me ini.
\v 10 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Duam iza Otniel giz…®vaz…®ma, a Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n iti. Ez…® a ghuava Mesopotemian atrivim ko m…®sosi, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Otniel…®n akuraz…®ma an atrivir kam ab…®ra.
\v 11 Egha g…®n, Israelia ua m…®dorozir tam gamir puvat…®gha ikia ghua 40plan azeniba g…®vaz…®ma, Kenas…®n otarim, Otniel, an areme.
\s1 Ehut gumazir dapanim…®n oto
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Israelia uamategha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n an aghuazir arazir kuram gami. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God gavgavir ekiam isa Moapian Atrivim Eklon gan…®ngiz…®ma, a Israelia ab…®ra.
\v 13 Eklon Amonia koma Amalekia akuvagha me ko akam ak…®righa ghua, Israelia m…®sogha me ab…®ragha, Temer Detba Itir Nguibar Ekiam ini.
\v 14 Ez…® Israelia, Atrivim Eklon…®n apengan ikia ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n ingara ghua 18plan azenibar tu.
\p 
\v 15 Egha Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha araima, a me bagh akurvazir gumazir mam am…®sefe, an ziam Ehut, an apaniba da ua me iniam. Ehut Benjamin…®n anabam…®n gumazir mam, a Geran otarim, an agharir k…®riam…®n ingarir gumazim. Dughiar kam…®n, Israelia bizir aghuir maba isa Moapian atrivim, Eklon bagha da amadima, Ehut da inigha ghu.
\v 16 Ehut faragha ua bagha m…®dorozir sabar ghumt…®zir pumuning itir mam…®n ingarigha, an m…®riamning v…®raram aning am…®ne. M…®dorozir sabar ghumt…®zir pumuning itir kam…®n ruarim 50 sentimitan tu. Egha dughiar an Atrivim Eklon bagha mangasava amim…®n, a m…®dorozir sabar ghumt…®zir pumuning itir kam isa uan agharir guvim…®n apengan buar ak…®rim…®n korotiar ruarim…®n aven a modo.
\v 17 Egha bizir aghuir kaba inigha Atrivim Eklon bagha zui. Eklon, a namnam saram aghungizir gumazir dafam.
\v 18 Ez…® Ehut ghua bizir aghuir kaba isava Eklon ganigha g…®vagha, a gumazir a ko bizir aghuiba atera ghuezir kaba ko, me uamatenge.
\p 
\v 19 Me ghua Gilgal…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n, dag…®abar gumazir nedazibar ingarigha da asezir danganim…®n otifi. Egha danganir kam…®n, Ehut Moapian atrivim…®n ganasa a bagha uamatenge. An Atrivim Eklon…®n ganigha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim, k…® n…® m…®k…®mamin m…®g…®r…®g…®ar mam iti, n…® uab…®ra a baragham.‚Äù Ez…® atrivim kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®, ga uaningra ikiam.‚Äù Ez…® ingangarir gumaziba bar mogh…®ra azenan ghue.
\v 20 Ez…® atrivim uab…®ra uan d…®penim…®n aven, an p…®n itir danganir orangt…®zim…®n avughsava ir…®ghav iti. Ez…® Ehut a bagha izava a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® God da izezir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar n…® m…®k…®mamin mam iti.‚Äù Ez…® atrivim d…®kavigha tuz…®ma,
\v 21 Ehut uan agharir k…®riam…®n, dafarir guvim…®n apengan korotiar ruarir aruzim…®n aven, buar ak…®rim gis…®n modozir sabam asigha, atrivim…®n navim gasara.
\v 22 Ez…® Ehut atrivim da sabar ghumt…®zir pumuning itim asizir puvat…®, an ghumt…®zim ko an m…®siam sara bar an navim…®n aven ghu. Ez…® an navim…®n ovim m…®dorozir sabam noke, ez…® a bar an aven ghua an ak…®rir agharim…®n tu.
\v 23 Ez…® Ehut d…®penim…®n aven avughsazir danganim ategha azuarim…®n azenan otogha deragha tiar akamning asaragha ghu.
\v 24 Ez…® g…®n an ingangarir gumaziba iza garima, me itiar akamning dukua. Ez…® me uarira uariv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúAtrivim ti uan avughsazir danganim…®n ikia uan davir danganim…®n aven ikiama.‚Äù
\v 25 Ez…® atrivim…®n ingangarir gumaziba uan atrivim m…®zua ikia ghua amia, me itiam kuigh aven mangan an amigha, bar dughiar ruarim…®n a m…®zua ghua ghaze, e uari aven mang…® ganigham. Egha me ki inigha tiam kuigha garima, Ame! Men gumazir aruam aremegha vazim…®n ir…®ghav iti!
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® ingangarir gumaziba pura gara itir dughiam…®n, Ehut arav ghugha g…®fa. An ara ghua, danganir me dag…®abar gumazir nedazibar ingarigha da asezim…®n otogha, dagh itagha, bar ara ghua Seiran nguibam…®n modo.
\p 
\v 27-28 Egha a g…®n azenim gir…®gha Seiran nguazim…®n ghua, Efraim…®n anababar m…®ghs…®ar dozibar otogha s…®gham givi, a men d…®mt…® me iz…® uari akuvagh mang…® m…®sogham. Israelia iza uari akuvaz…®, Ehut kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa nan g…®n iz…®. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian apaniba, Moapia isa ian agharim gat…®gha g…®fa. Ia me ab…®ragham.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me m…®ghs…®ar dozibar itir nguibaba ategha, Ehut…®n g…®n uaghira Moapia bagha Jordan…®n Fanem…®n men arafa, eght…® men tav fanem gir…®gh vong…®n mangan kogham. Ez…® me Moapian m…®sozima, men tav arav ghuzir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.
\v 29 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Israelia Moapian 10,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavibav soghez…® me ariaghire. Tav arav ghuzir puvat…®.
\v 30 Kamagh…®ra, Israelia dughiar kam…®n Moapia gafiragha, ua m…®dorozir tam gamizir puvat…®gha ghua 80plan azenibar tu.
\s1 Samgar gumazir dapanim…®n oto
\p 
\v 31 Gumazir dapanim Ehut…®n g…®n, gumazir dapanir igharazim oto, an ziam Samgar, an Anat…®n otarim. Me zuam…®ra ingangarim damuasa bulmakaubar av…®zir aghorir mam, an a isa, Filistiabar 600plan gumazibav soghez…® me ariaghire. A uaghan apanibar agharim…®n ua Israelia ini.
\c 4
\ms1 Deboran eghaghanim
\mr (Sapta 4--5)
\s1 Debora ko Barak apaniba ab…®ra
\p 
\v 1 Ehut aremez…®, Israelia ua God…®n damazim…®n an aghuazir arazir kurabagh ami.
\v 2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God Jabin ataghiz…®, a uaghan me ab…®ra. Jabin, a Kenanian atrivir mam, egha Hasor…®n nguibam…®n garir atrivim. Atrivim Jabin, an m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim Sisera, a nguibar ekiam Haroset Hagoim…®n gumazir mam.
\v 3 Atrivim Jabin, ain…®n m…®dorozir karis…®n 900pla iti. A bar pazav…®ra Israelia gamuava, tintinibar me m…®sogha me gas…®ghas…®gha ghua 20plan azenibar tu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelia uarir akurvaghasa Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha arai.
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, God…®n akam inigha izir amizir mam iti, an ziam Debora. A gumazir mam…®n amuim, an ziam Lapidot. Dughiar kam Debora amizir dapanim…®n ikia n…®ghn…®ziba isa Israelia gan…®di.
\v 5 Debora zurara Temer Det…®n Povim…®n apiav itima, Israelia uan os…®mt…®ziba inigha a bagha izima, a kot…®n aven men os…®mt…®ziba tuis…®zima, me an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba barasi. Temer kam, Rama ko Betel…®n nguibar ekiamning…®n tizim…®n, Efraim…®n anabam…®n nguazim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozim…®n iti.
\p 
\v 6 Dughiar mam Debora Barak…®n dei, a Kedes…®n nguibam…®n Naptalin anabam…®n nguazim…®n itir gumazir mam, Abinoam…®n otarim. Egha Barak izima, Debora kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, a m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam n…® dan…®ngasa, ‚ÄòN…® mang…® Naptalin anabam ko Sebulun…®n anabam…®n gumazir 10,000pla inigh iz…® Tabor…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n me akufagh.
\v 7 K…® Sisera inigh izam, an Atrivim Jabin…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanim. A iz…® Kison…®n Fanem…®n ia ko m…®sogham. A uan m…®dorozir karisba ko uan m…®dorozir gumazir av…®riba inigh iz…®t…®, k…® me is…® ian agharim dar…®gham.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Barak akar kam baregha kamagh…®n Deboran m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® na ko mang…®t…®, k…® mangam. N…® na ko mangan koght…®, k…® mangan kogham.‚Äù
\v 9 Ez…® Debora kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra n…® ko mangam. Eght…® m…®dorozir kam…®n aven Ikiav…®ra Itir God Sisera is…® amizitam…®n agharim dar…®gham. Kamagh…®ra, n…®rara, m…®dorozir kam bagh ziar ekiam inian kogham. Puvat…®.‚Äù Egha Debora d…®kavigha Barak ko Kedes…®n nguibam…®n zui.
\v 10 Ez…® Barak Sebulun…®n anabam ko Naptalin anabam…®n gumazibar diagha Kedes…®n zui. Dughiar kam 10,000plan gumaziba a ko m…®soghasa zui. Ez…® Debora uaghan me ko zui.
\v 11 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Heber a Kinian adarazir mav, a Kinia ataki, me Moses…®n ivozir afeziam Hobap, an ovavir boriba, a me ategha ghua uan averpenim Kedes…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n, Sananim…®n itir ok…®n temer ekiam…®n borogh…®n an ingari.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Sisera kamagh…®n oraki, Abinoam…®n otarim Barak ghua Tabor…®n M…®ghs…®am…®n ghuanabo.
\v 13 Egha Sisera uan 900plan ain…®n karisba ko uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar men diagha, me inigha Kison…®n Faner gigir d…®paba pura datim…®n borogh…®n, Haroset Hagoim…®n nguibam…®n zui.
\v 14 Ez…® Debora kamagh…®n Barak m…®gei, ‚ÄúAria, n…® d…®kavigh, e mangam. Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n faragh mangam. Dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n akuragh, Sisera is…® n…®n agharim dat…®gham.‚Äù Ez…® Barak zuam…®ra 10,000plan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha Tabor…®n M…®ghs…®am ategha uaghiri.
\v 15 Barak uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua otogha m…®dorozim forezir dughiam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God men damazim…®n Sisera gamiz…®, an ain…®n karisba ko m…®dorozir gumaziba bar ongani. Ez…® Sisera uan karis ategha uan suemning…®n arav ghu.
\v 16 Ez…® Barak men karisba ko m…®dorozir gumazibar ag…®ragha ghua, Haroset…®n Hagoim…®n nguibam…®n oto. Egha Barak…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, Siseran m…®dorozir gumazibav soghez…® me bar ariaghire, men tav ua itir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 17 Ez…® Sisera ara ghua Jael…®n averpenim…®n ghu, a Heber…®n amuim, Kin…®n adarazir mav. Hasor…®n nguibam…®n Atrivim Jabin, a Heber…®n adarazir namakar aghuim, me derav…®ra uari inigha ikia, uariv sozir puvat…®.
\v 18 Dughiar kam…®n, Jael Siseran gari a izima, Jael averpenim ategha azenan iza kamagh…®n Sisera m…®gei, ‚ÄúO nan gumazir aruam, n…® aven iz…® daperagh. N…® nan averpenim…®n aven iz…® avughsam. N…® atiatingan mark…®.‚Äù Ez…®, Sisera Jael…®n averpenim…®n aven ghuz…®ma, Jael nir m…®tiar mam inigha anevara.
\v 19 Ez…® Sisera Jael m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúNan kuarim nan p…®ri. N…® d…®patam na dan…®ngight…® k…® anemeka.‚Äù Ez…® Jael memen nir me d…®paba tuasa isamizir, memen oter eborim itir mam kuigha, a isa a gan…®ngi. Ez…® Sisera anemez…®, Jael uam anevaragha a modo.
\v 20 Ez…® Sisera kamagh…®n Jael m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® averpenim…®n tiar akam…®n tugh…®v ik…®t…®, gumazitam iz…® n…®n azaragham, ‚ÄòGumazitam kagh iti?‚Äô Eght…® n…® kamagh…®n a m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄòPuvat…®.‚Äô ‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Ez…® Siseran m…®karzim bar an am…®raz…® ana aremez…® mogh…®n akui. Ez…® Jael dafarir vuem…®n averpenibar benibar suizir afughafuzir mam…®n suira, egha dafarir vuem…®n ingangarir gumazibar haman suiragha, bar aghumra Siseran amuda zui. An haman suiragha ghua afughafuzir kam isa Siseran dakurum gasaragha, afughafuzim gafuz…®, a bar anem…®k…®ragha nguazim giraghu. Ez…® Sisera areme.
\v 22 Dughiar kam…®n, Barak Sisera buria izima, Jael ghua a batogha kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® iz…®t…®, k…® n…® inigh mang…® gumazir n…® ruiagha aruim, n…®n akagham.‚Äù Ez…® Barak a ko averpenim…®n aven ghua garima, Sisera aremegha g…®vagha ir…®ghav itima, afughafuzir kam an dakurum…®n m…®goroghav ikia mamagh…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n God Israelian akuragha, men damazim…®n Kenanian Atrivim Jabin ab…®raz…®, a bar aghums…®ki.
\v 24 Ez…® Israelia m…®sogha ghua bar gavgavigha Kenanian atrivim Jabin ko an m…®dorozir gumazibagh as…®ghas…®ki.
\c 5
\s1 Debora ko Barak…®n onger akam
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam Debora ko Abinoam…®n otarim Barak, aning ighiar kam bange:
\b
\q1 
\v 2 E Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fam.
\q1 Israelian gumazir dapaniba d…®kavigha derav…®ra gumazamizibar faragha ghua, pamten m…®soghasa n…®ghn…®si.
\q2 Ez…® gumazamiziba m…®soghasa pamtem…®n n…®ghn…®gha bar akonge.
\q2 E Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fam!
\q1 
\v 3 Ia atriviba, oragh!
\q2 Ia gumazir dapaniba, ia derav…®ra kuariba ar…®gh oragh!
\q1 K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ighiatam bang…®va marvibagh iviam.
\q2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, k…® a g…®n…®ghn…®gh ighiam damuam.
\q1 
\v 4 O Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® Seir…®n M…®ghs…®am ataghizir dughiam,
\q2 kar Idom…®n nguazim,
\q3 n…® izaghirima,
\q2 m…®k…®mk…®zim nguazim g…®nobaz…®,
\q3 amozim arigha m…®ghs…®abar izaghiri.
\q2 Bar guizbang…®ra, d…®par dafam overiam…®n ghuariabar ikegha
\q3 nguazim…®n izaghiri.
\b
\q1 
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Ua Me Ini 19:18\x*M…®ghs…®aba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n vazvasi,
\q2 a Sainaian God,
\q2 a Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God.
\b
\q1 
\v 6 Anat…®n otarim Samgar…®n dughiam,
\q2 ko Jael…®n dughiam,
\q1 gumazir dag…®aba bagha biziba amadiba,
\q2 me ok…®mak…®ar gumazibar atiatia uamategha tuavir ekiam…®n aruir puvat…®.
\q1 Me mang…® zegh gamua,
\q2 egha moga k…®riar tuavir dozibagh arui.
\b
\q1 
\v 7 O Debora, Israel…®n kantrin nguibar doziba itir gumazamiziba, me bizitam gamizir puvat…®.
\q2 Me pura ikia ghua dughiar n…® otozim…®n tu.
\q1 Guizbang…®ra, n…® Israelian tong…®n ikia mati men ganamin amebar mam.
\b
\q1 
\v 8 Ez…® Israelia aser igiabar g…®n zuir dughiam…®n,
\q2 m…®doroziba me batifi.
\q1 Israelia m…®dorozir gumazir 40,000pla iti,
\q2 egha me bar mogh…®ra m…®soghamin oraba ko afuziba puvat…®.
\b
\q1 
\v 9 K…® uan navir averiam…®n aven, Israelian m…®dorozir gumazibar faragha zuir gumazir dapanibagh n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra iti.
\q2 Guizbang…®ra, men marazi uari isa m…®dorozim gan…®di.
\q1 Kamagh…®n, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fam.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Ia gumazir donkin ghurghuribar satelbagh apiaghiriba,
\q2 ko ia uan suebar tuavibagh aruir gumaziba,
\q3 ia bizir kam…®n gun m…®k…®m.
\q1 
\v 11 Ia oragh! Gumazamizir mozir d…®paba uari akuvava d…®paba isava sipsipbagh an…®diba,
\q2 me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, an arazir aghuibara amuava apaniba ab…®ra.
\q1 Egha me uaghan ghaze, Israel…®n kantrin nguibar doziba itir gumazamiziba, bar deragha apanibagh afira.
\q2 Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamiziba uan nguibaba ategha, izaghira nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n ize.
\q1 
\v 12 O Debora, n…® osegh d…®kavigh en faragh mang…®.
\q2 N…® faragh mang…® ighiatam bang…®!
\q1 O Abinoam…®n otarim Barak, n…® d…®kafigh!
\q2 N…® m…®dorozim gafiragh apaniba d…®kab…®ragh.
\q2 Egh n…® m…®dorozim…®n aven iniamin kalabuziar gumazir kaba inigh, men aku iz…®.
\q1 
\v 13 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir aghuir ikiav…®ra itiba, izaghira uan gumazir dapaniba ko uari akufi.
\q2 Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamiziba a bagha iza m…®soghasa uari akufi.
\q1 
\v 14 Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazi izaghira danganir zarim…®n oto,
\q2 Efraim…®n adarazi fom…®ra Amalekia ab…®ragha men nguazim ini.
\q1 Me dat…®r…®gh…®n Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazir g…®n zui.
\q2 Ez…® Makir…®n adarazir gumazir dapaniba uaghan izaghiri.
\q1 Ez…® Sebulun…®n anabam…®n gumazir dapaniba uan ghuarar gavgavibar suigha izaghiri.
\q1 
\v 15 Ez…® Isakar…®n anabam…®n gumazir dapaniba Debora ko izi.
\q1 Isakar…®n anabam…®n gumazir kaba derav…®ra Barak…®n g…®n zuima,
\q2 a men faragha ghua zuam…®ra danganir zarim…®n zui.
\q1 Ez…® Ruben…®n anabam…®n adarazi n…®ghn…®zir pumuning ikia mangan aghua.
\q1 
\v 16 Ia Ruben…®n anabam…®n adarasi, ia tizim bagha sipsipba ko ikiav…®ra iti?
\q1 Ia sipsipbar garir gumaziba, ia ti sipsipbar deir buaber d…®mdiam baraghasa?
\q1 Bar guizbang…®ra, Ruben…®n anabam…®n adarazi
\q2 n…®ghn…®zir pumuning iti.
\b
\q1 
\v 17 Ez…® Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n itir adarasi, me pura Jordan…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n ikiav…®ra iti.
\q2 Ez…® Dan…®n anabam…®n adarasi, bizir tizim bagha kuribar ingari?
