\v 30 Ez…® me kamagh…®n Joas m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n otarim, asem Bal…®n ofa gamir dakozim ko, aser amizim Aseran temer ak…®nir ekiar an borogh…®n m…®t…®ghav itim ap…®riaghat…®. Kamagh…®n, n…® a inigh kagh iz…®t…®, e a m…®sueght…® an a aremegham.‚Äù
