\v 31 Ez…® Joas kamagh…®n gumazir an ataribar akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa asem Bal…®n akurvaghasa na gimobi? Gumazir manam asem Bal…®n akurvaghasa na dosi, aruem t…®ghar anangamin dughiam…®n an a aremegham. Ofa gamir dakozir me d…®p…®rizir kam, kar Bal…®n ofa gamir dakozim. Kamagh…®n, Bal guizbang…®ra god, a uab…® uab…®n akuragh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 32 Dughiar kam…®n ikegha zui, Gideon ziar igiam iti. An afeziam Joas kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGideon as…®ghas…®ghizir ofa gamir dakozir kam, kar Bal…®n bizim. Kamagh…®n, Bal uab…® uab…®n akuragh.‚Äù Kamagh…®n, me ‚ÄúJerubal,‚Äù Gideon gat…®.\f + \fr 6:32 \ft Ziar kam Jerubal, an tiarim Hibrun akam…®n kamagh…®n ghu, ‚ÄúBal uab…® uab…®n akuragh.‚Äù\f*
\p 
\v 33 Dughiar kam…®n, Midian…®n adarazi ko Amalekia, ko aruem anadi nagh…®n itir gumazamiziba, me uari akuvagha iti. Egha me Jordan…®n Fanem abigha vong…®n ghua, Jesril…®n danganir zarim…®n averpenibar ingarigha dar iti.
\v 34 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Duam iza Gideon avaragha an itima, a d…®kavigha, Abieser…®n adarazir diaght…® me iz…® an g…®n mangasa, a sipsip…®n kom…®n ingarizir s…®gham givi.
\v 35 A uaghan gumazir maba amadaz…®, me ghua Manasen anabam…®n nguazim…®n itir adaraziv g…®a ghaze, me iz…® an g…®n mangam. A uaghan Aser ko Sebulun ko Naptalin anababar adarazir m…®k…®masa, gumazir maba amangi. Ez…® me uaghan d…®kavigha iza a ko uari akufa.
\p 
\v 36 Ez…® Gideon kamagh…®n God m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® na m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® na damut…® k…® Israelian akuragham, k…® bar guiz…®n foghasa n…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam a guizbang…®ra, ga uaning, n…® arazitam nan akagh.
\v 37 N…® gan, danganir e wit…®n dafariba am…®sevim…®n, k…® sipsip…®n ar…®zitaba nguazim dar…®gham. Eght…® m…®zaraghara ghuariar d…®pam sipsip…®n ar…®zir kabar ik…®va, egh nguazim gireghan koght…®, k…® kamagh…®n fogh suam, mati n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, k…® Israelian akurvagham.‚Äù
\v 38 Ez…® bizir kam, Gideon God ko m…®kemez…® mogh…®n oto. Ez…® Gideon m…®zaraghara osegha d…®kavigha ghua sipsip…®n ar…®zir an at…®zim…®n ganasa zui. Egha sipsip…®n ar…®zim ghavk…®ra an gari, d…®pam an iti, o puvat…®. Ez…® d…®pam a giz…®fa, an an munumut…®, d…®pam itarir ekiatam giz…®vagham.
\p 
\v 39 Egha g…®n Gideon ua ghua kamagh…®n God m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® nan ataran mark…®. K…® ua m…®g…®r…®g…®atam damuasa. Ga uaning, k…® kamaghsua, n…® na ateght…®, k…® ua sipsip…®n ar…®zim damigh an ganika. Eght…® dughiar kam…®n ghuariar d…®paba tintinibar nguazim giregh, eght…® sipsip…®n ar…®zimra m…®s…®ngigh ik…®.‚Äù
\v 40 Ez…® d…®magarir kam…®n, God, Gideon m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami. Sipsip…®n ar…®zimra m…®s…®ngiz…®, nguazim, ghuariam bar a gire.
\c 7
\s1 Gideon Midiania gafira
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Jerubal, kar Gideon uab…®, a uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko bar m…®zaraghara d…®kavigha ghua, Harot…®n em…®m…®rim…®n m…®riam…®n averpenibar ingarigha iti. Ez…® Midianian averpeniba, Moren m…®ghs…®am…®n borogh…®n danganir zarim…®n, Gideon…®n amadaghan not…®n iti.
