\v 2 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n Gideon m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ian akuragh Midiania m…®soghasa ifonge. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazir bar av…®rim n…® ko iti. Me ti kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gh suam, ‚ÄòE uarira, uan gavgavibar Midiania m…®sogh me ab…®ragham.‚Äô Egh me uan ziaba fam. Me ti kamagh…®n n…®ghnigh, egh kamagh…®n m…®kemeghan kogham, k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® men akuragham.
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt God…®n Araziba 20:8\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® kamagh…®n me m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòGumazir manam atiati, a Gileat…®n M…®ghs…®am ategh uamategh uan nguibam…®n mang…®.‚Äô ‚Äù Ez…® Gideon kamagh…®n me tuis…®gha, me m…®kemez…®ma, 22,000plan m…®dorozir gumaziba d…®kavigha uamategha ghue. Ez…® 10,000plan m…®dorozir gumaziba ikiav…®ra iti.
