\v 24 Ez…® Gideon uaghan Efraim…®n anabam…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar tintinibar itir gumaziba bagha akam amada. A kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa izighir…® e Midianian adarazi ko m…®sogham. Egh ia mang…® Jordan…®n Fanem…®n me bagh p…®gh…®va, daghurir doziba ko em…®m…®ribar me bagh gan mang…® Betbaran nguibam…®n me bagh gan men suikigh. Puvat…®ght…®ma, me Jordan…®n Fanem giregh vong…®n mangegham.‚Äù
