\v 3 \x - \xo 8:3-5 \xt Onger Akaba 83:11\x*Guizbang…®ra, God Midianian m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanir pumuning isa ian agharim gat…®, aning…®n ziamning Orep ko Sep. Ez…® ia aning…®n f…®rimning atu. Bizir kam bar ekefe. K…® kamagh…®n garir bizitam gamizir puvat…®.‚Äù Gideon kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®vaz…®, Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazi uam an atari puvat…®.
