\v 21 Ez…® Seba ko Salmuna kamagh…®n Gideon m…®gei, ‚ÄúE fo, gumazir aruaba uari kamagh…®n bizim damus…®, me uan gavgavibar amodogh…®n a damuam. Kamagh…®n, n…® uab…® iz…® ga m…®sogh.‚Äù Kamagh…®n, Gideon uab…® Seba ko Salmuna m…®soghez…®, aning areme. Egha an aning…®n kamelning…®n f…®rim…®n itir benir iak…®nir igiam…®n nedazim guraghav itir adiarimning ini.\f + \fr 8:21 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
