\v 23 \x - \xo 8:23 \xt 1 Samuel 8:7; 10:19; 12:12\x*Ez…® Gideon kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ian gumazir dapanim…®n ikian kogham. Eght…® nan otarim uaghan, ian gumazir dapanim…®n ikian kogham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a uab…® ian gumazir dapanim…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\v 24 Gideon fo, Midiania me Ismael…®n ovavir boribar adarasi, me ringba uan kuaribagh ar…®si.
\p Kamagh…®n, a m…®g…®a ghua ua kamagh…®n Israelia m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® bizir mam bagh ian azangasa. Ia bar mogh…®ra m…®dorozim…®n Midianian kuaribar guizir ring…®n iniziba, ia vaghvagh dar vam…®ra vam…®ra is…® na dan…®ngam.‚Äù
