\v 28 Kamagh…®ra, Israelia m…®dorozim…®n Midianian adarazi ab…®ragha aghums…®zir ekiam me gan…®ngi. Ez…® Midianian adarazi ua bizitam damuan ibura. Kamagh…®n, Gideon ikiav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, Israelia ua m…®dorozir tam gamizir puvat…®gha ghua 40plan azenibar tu.
\s1 Gideon areme
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® Joas…®n otarim Jerubal, an ziar mam Gideon, a ghua uan nguibam…®n itir d…®penim…®n iti.
\v 30 An amuir av…®riba iti, egha bizir kam bang…®n, a 70plan otariba iti.
\v 31 Ez…® Gideon…®n amuir dozir mam Sekem…®n nguibam…®n iti. An amuir kam otarir mam batez…®, Gideon ziam, ‚ÄúAbimelek,‚Äù a gat…®.
\v 32 Ez…® Joas…®n otarim Gideon bar ghurigha areme. Ez…® me Abieser…®n adarazir nguibam Ofran, an afeziam Joas afaz…® nagh…®n, uaghan anefa.
\p 
\v 33 Gideon aremez…®, Israelia zuam…®ra ua God…®n ziam fer puvat…®. Me mati tuavim…®n amizim tintinim…®n gumaziba koma akua da bagha arui mogh…®n, aser Balbar, ziaba fe. Egha asem Balberit at…®z…®, a men god…®n oto.
\v 34 Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uam a g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. A men God, a men akuraz…®, men apaniba tintinibar iza me m…®sozir dughiabar, me me ab…®ni.
\v 35 Guizbang…®ra, Jerubal, an ziar mam Gideon, a deraghav…®ra men akuragha me bagha bizir aghuir av…®ribagh ami. Ez…® me da bak…®n…®gh…®nigha, derav…®ra Gideon…®n adarazi ikaragha me m…®nabazir puvat…®.
\c 9
\s1 Abimelek Sekem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n atrivim…®n oto
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Abimelek Jerubal…®n otarim, kar Gideonra, a uan amebam…®n adarazi ko amebam…®n anabam…®n gumazamiziba bar men ganasa Sekem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghugha,
\v 2 kamagh…®n men azai, ‚ÄúIa manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®si? Jerubal…®n otarir 70pla e gativagh, en faragh mangam, o? Ia ti gumazir vam…®rara ateght…® a en gumazir dapanim…®n ikiam? Ia deraghv…®ra n…®ghn…®gh, k…® Abimelek, k…® ian inivaf…®zimra. Ia bizir kam deraghv…®ra an gun m…®k…®mt…®, Sekem…®n gumazir aruaba ian n…®ghn…®zim baragham.‚Äù
\v 3 Ez…® Abimelek…®n amebam…®n adarazi m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam inigha ghua Sekem…®n gumazir aruabav kemez…®ma, me oregha a gifonge. Me ghaze, a men anabamra.
