\v 8 Ez…® Gileat…®n gumazir aruaba kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúMar guizbang…®ra. E dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® iniasa izi, n…® en g…®n mang…®va en akuragh Amonia ko m…®sogham. Egh n…® g…®n Gileat…®n gumazamizibar gumazir dapanim…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Jepta kamagh…®n Gileat…®n gumazir aruabav gei, ‚ÄúAre! Ia na inigh uamategh mang…®ght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God nan akuraght…®ma, k…® m…®dorozim damuva apaniba ab…®raght…®, ia guiz…®n na ateght…® k…® ian gumazir dapanim…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® gumazir aruaba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra, e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n n…® m…®gei, e n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®ra e damuam.‚Äù
\v 11 Kamagh…®n, Jepta Gileat…®n gumazir aruaba ko zui. Ez…® gumazamiziba anem…®sevez…®ma, a men gumazir dapanim…®n iti. Ez…® Jepta Mispan nguibam…®n ikia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n m…®t…®gha uan akam…®n gumazamizibav gei.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Jepta g…®n Amonian atrivim kamagh…®n an azangasa gumaziba amada, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha iza nan atara nan nguazim iniasa na ko m…®sosi?‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Amonian atrivim kamagh…®n gumazir Jepta amadazibar azangs…®ghizir akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIsraelia faragha Isip…®n kantri ategha izava nan nguazim okeme, an Arnon…®n Fanem…®n ikegha ghua, Jabok…®n Fanem…®n otogha, ghua Jordan…®n Fanem…®n tu. Ez…® k…® bizir kam baghava atari. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n nan nguazim is…® ua na dan…®ngam. Puvat…®ght…®, e uariv sogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Jepta ua gumaziba amadaz…®, me Amonian atrivim bagha zui.
\v 15 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúJepta ghaze, puvat…®, Israelia Moapian nguazim ko Amonian nguazim okemezir puvat…®.
\v 16 Israelia Isip ategha izir dughiam…®n me gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n izava Ongarir Aghevim…®n otifi. Egha me g…®n ghuava Kades…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto.
\v 17 \x - \xo 11:17 \xt D…®boboniba 20:14-21\x*Egha Israelia uamategha gumazir kaba amangiz…® me ghuava kamagh…®n Idomian atrivim…®n azangs…®si, ‚ÄòE uari, n…® e ateght…® e n…®n nguazim abigh mang…® vong…®n otivigham, o puvat…®gham?‚Äô Ez…® atrivim aghua. Ez…® me gumaziba amangiz…®ma me ghua Moapian atrivim…®n azai. Ez…® a uaghan aghua. Kamagh…®n, Israelia Kades…®n ikia iti.
\p 
\v 18 \x - \xo 11:18 \xt D…®boboniba 21:4\x*‚ÄúEgha me g…®n ghua gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n zui. Egha me Idom ko Moapian nguazim…®n ghuzir puvat…®. Me Moap…®n, aruem anadi nagh…®n Arnon…®n Fanem…®n vong…®n kagh…®ra iti. Me an averpenibar ingarigha iti, kar men nguazir m…®taghniam. Kamagh…®n, me Arnon…®n Fanem abigha vong…®n ghuezir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 19 \x - \xo 11:19-22 \xt D…®boboniba 21:21-24\x*‚ÄúEz…® Amorian atrivim, Sihon, a Hesbon…®n danganim…®n itima, Israelia mang…® an ganasa gumaziba amangi. Ez…® me kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄòE uari, n…® kamagh…®n ifonge, e n…®n nguazim abigh mang…® vong…®n otivam o markiam? E uan nguazim a baghv…®ra mangasa.‚Äô
\v 20 Ez…® Sihon aghua. Egha uan m…®dorozir gumaziba bar me inigha ghua, Jahas…®n nguibar ekiam…®n averpenibar ingarigha dar ikiava Israelia ko m…®sosi.
\v 21 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, a Israelian akuragha Sihon…®n adarazi ko men m…®dorozir gumaziba sara bar me ab…®ra. Kamagh…®n, Israelia Amorian nguazir danganir me itir kabanang bar ada ini.
\p 
\v 22 ‚ÄúMe bar Amorian nguaziba ini, me saut…®n amadaghan Arnon…®n Fanem…®n ikegha, ghua not…®n amadaghan Jabok…®n Fanem…®n tu, egha aruem anadi nagh…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n ikegha ghua, aruem uaghiri nagh…®n Jordan…®n Fanem…®n tu.
\v 23 Kamagh…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, a uab…® Amoria batuegha, men nguazim isava uan gumazamizibagh an…®ngi. Kar Israelia. Ez…® n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ua nguazir kam iniasa?
\v 24 N…® uan bizir n…®n asem Kemos n…® gan…®ngiziba, n…® da ini. Ez…® en nguazir en God e gan…®ngiziba, da en nguaziba.
\p 
\v 25 \x - \xo 11:25 \xt D…®boboniba 22:1-6\x*‚ÄúEz…® manmagh…®n ami? N…® ghaze n…®n gavgavim ti Balak…®n gavgavim gafira? A Sipor…®n otarim, egha Moapian atrivim. A nguazir taba ua uab…® dan…®ngasa m…®geir puvat…®. Egha e ko m…®dorozim gamizir puvat…®.
\v 26 Ez…® Israelia Hesbon ko Aroer…®n nguibamning isava, aning…®n borogh…®n itir nguibar doziba isava, egha Arnon…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n itir nguibar ekiaba bar ada inigha, 300plan azenibar dagh apiaghav iti. Manmagh…®n amiz…® ia dughiar kam…®n ua nguibar kaba inigha dagh apiazir puvat…®?
\v 27 Ez…® Jepta kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, an arazir kuratam n…® gamizir puvat…®. N…® uab…® arazir kuram gamigha a ko m…®sosi. God uab…® gumazibar araziba tuis…®si, a dat…®r…®gh…®n bar mogh…®ra ia ko en araziba tuis…®gham.‚Äù
\v 28 Ez…® Amonian atrivim akar Jepta a bagha amadazir kam baraghizir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Duam Jepta giz…®vaz…®ma, a uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha, me Gileat ko Manasen anabam…®n nguazim…®n ghua Gileat…®n aven Mispan otifi, egha g…®n Mispan nguazim ategha ghuava Amonian nguazim…®n oto.
\v 30 Ez…® Jepta Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n akar mam ak…®righa ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® nan akuraght…® k…® m…®dorozim…®n Amonia ab…®nigh,
\v 31 egh m…®dorozim…®n ikegh uamategh izamin dughiar kam…®n, bizir manam faragh nan d…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n azenim gir…®gh, na bagh izamim bizir kam, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizim…®n otivam. Eght…® k…® a is…® ofan bar isi m…®gh…®rim…®n m…®n n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\v 32 Ez…® Jepta uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko fanem abigha ghua Amonia bativigha me m…®sosi. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Jeptan akuraz…®ma me m…®dorozim…®n me ab…®ra.
\v 33 Me Amonia m…®sogha bar me ab…®ni, me Aroer…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikegha me m…®sogha ghua Minit…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha, bar ghua Abel Keramim…®n d…®pam…®n tu. Me 20plan nguibabav sogha, me ab…®ragha bar me ag…®fa. Kamagh…®ra Israelia bar Amonia ab…®nigha, aghums…®zim me gan…®ngiz…®, me ua me ko m…®soghan ibura.
\s1 Jepta uan akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamiz…® a guizbang…®ram oto
\p 
\v 34 Ez…® Jepta uamategha uan nguibam…®n iza Mispan nguibar ekiam…®n otoz…®, an guivim d…®penim ategha ivegha a bagha zui. A bar akongegha uan tambarin m…®sogha ighiam bangava ighavamaga izi. Guizbang…®ra, Jepta guivir kamra iti. A ua boriba puvat…®.
\v 35 \x - \xo 11:35 \xt D…®boboniba 30:2\x*Ez…® Jepta uan guivim…®n ganigha, bar d…®gavir kuram gamigha uan korotiam abigha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO nan guivim, noka! N…® bar nan d…®ghorim ab…®ki. K…® bar oseme. N…® tizim bagha faragha iza na batogha os…®mt…®zir ekiam na gan…®ngi? K…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamigha g…®fa, egh k…® anebighan kogham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 36 Ez…® an guivim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO nan afeziam, n…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n akam ak…®righa g…®fa. Kamagh…®n, n…® akam ak…®righa g…®vaz…® mogh…®n, n…® na damu. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n akuraz…®, n…® uan apaniba Amonia ab…®ra.‚Äù
\p 
\v 37 Egha a kamagh…®n uan afeziam m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® kamaghsua, n…® faragh na ateght…® k…® uan namakaba ko iak…®nir pumuning…®n m…®ghs…®abar orazibar daru azir akabar amuam. K…® fo, k…® gumazitam…®n ikeghan kogh borir tam bateghan kogh…®va aremegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 38 Ez…® an afeziam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúA dera, n…® mang…®.‚Äù Egha anemadaz…® a ghua iak…®nir pumuning…®n ike. A uan namakaba ko ghua m…®ghs…®abagh arua, azir akabagh amua kamagh…®n azi, a gumazitam…®n ikeghan kogh…®va borir taba inighan kogh aremegham.\f + \fr 11:38 \ft Gumazitam God ko akam ak…®ri, a bizir bar ekiam. N…® Jems 5:12 ko Matyu 5:33-37…®n gan. Jepta deragha n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®gha onganigha akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam gami. Kar bar arazir kuram an a gami. God…®n Akar Gavgavim…®n, God ghaze, gumazamiziba uan boribar ofa damuan kogham. Ofa Gami 20:2…®n gan. Jepta amizir bizir kam, a kamagh…®n en aka, a bar derav…®ra God…®n Akar Gavgavibar g…®n zuir puvat…®. A bar arazir kuram gami.\f*
\v 39 Ez…® iak…®nir pumuning g…®vaz…®ma a uamategha iza uan afeziam bato, ez…® an afeziam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n akam ak…®riz…® mogh…®n, a gami. Ez…® guivir kam gumazitam ko akuizir puvat…®. Ez…® arazir kam bang…®n, Israelia zurara arazir kam gami.
\p 
\v 40 Israelian guivir igiaba, zurara azeniba bar, dar dughiar 4plan, me Jeptan guivim g…®n…®ghn…®gha osemegha aruava a bagha azi.
\c 12
\s1 Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazi Gileatia ko m…®sosi
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazi uari akuvagha m…®dorozim damuasa, m…®dorozir biziba inigha Jordan…®n Fanem giregha vong…®n otogha, Safon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n zui. Me ghua kamagh…®n Jepta m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Amonia ko m…®soghasa Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gha vong…®n zuir dughiam…®n, n…® en d…®man aghua? N…® oragh, bizir kam bang…®n, e dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® ko n…®n d…®penim dapongam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® Jepta kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® uan adarazi ko, e Amonia ko adarir ekiam iti. Egha k…® ian diaz…®, ia iza nan akurazir puvat…®.
\v 3 Ez…® k…® gari ia iza nan akurazir puvat…®z…®, k…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄòK…® mang…® Amonia ko m…®soght…®, me mar na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeka.‚Äô Kamagh…®n, k…® Jordan…®n Fanem gir…®gha anebigha ghua m…®dorozim foregha a gami. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God nan akuraz…®ma k…® m…®dorozim…®n me ab…®ra. Ez…® ia dat…®r…®gh…®n tizim bagha iza na m…®soghasa?‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Efraimian anabam…®n adarasi, faragha Gileat…®n adaraziv g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa Gileat…®n adarasi, ia Efraim…®n nguazim…®n ikegha ara iza, dat…®r…®gh…®n Efraim ko Manasen nguazimning…®n t…®zimning…®n iti. Egha ia gumazamizir pura guighav itiba.‚Äù Kamagh…®n, Jepta Gileat…®n gumaziba bar me akuvagha, Efraim…®n gumazibav sogha me ab…®ri.\f + \fr 12:4 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® Gileat…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba Efraim…®n gumaziba bagha p…®gha, Jordan…®n Fanem ab…®gha ghua otivir tuavir akabar iti. Ez…® Efraim…®n gumaziba m…®dorozim…®n ara fanem…®n iza kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE d…®pam giregh vong…®n mangasa.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Gileat…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba kamagh…®n vaghvagha men azangs…®si, ‚ÄúN…® Efraim…®n tav o puvat…®?‚Äù
\p Eght…® me kamagh…®n m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúPuvat…®,‚Äù eght…® me ua kamagh…®n a m…®k…®mam,
\v 6 ‚ÄúAria n…® m…®k…®m, ‚ÄòSihibolet.‚Äô ‚Äù Eght…® gumazir kam deragh ziar kam d…®ponan kogh, suam, ‚ÄúSibolet,‚Äù eght…® me fogh suam kar Efraim…®n adarazir gumazir mam, egh me an suiragh a m…®sueght…® an aremegham. Me kamagh…®n amua ghua Jordan…®n Fanem g…®ra iza, otivir tuavir akabar p…®gha, Efraim…®n adarazir 42,000plan gumazibav soghez…® me ariaghire.\f + \fr 12:6 \ft Hibrun akam…®n akar kam kamak…®n, ‚ÄúSihibolet,‚Äù o ‚ÄúSibolet,‚Äù an m…®ngarim kamak…®n, ‚Äúraiziar dapanim.‚Äù Gileatia kamagh…®n ziar kam d…®bori, ‚ÄúSihibolet.‚Äù Ez…® Efraim…®n adarazir ighara a d…®bori, ‚ÄúSibolet.‚Äù Gumazitam, deragh Gileatian adarazi a d…®bori mogh…®n, a deragh a d…®boroghan koght…®, me fogham kar Efraim…®n gumazir mam, egh me an m…®sueght…® ana aremegham.\f*
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Gileatian gumazim Jepta, a 6plan azenibar Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n ikegha areme. Ez…® me Gileat…®n nguazim…®n anefa.\f + \fr 12:7 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\s1 Ipsan, gumazir dapanim…®n oto
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Jepta aremez…®, g…®n, Betlehem…®n gumazim Ipsan, a Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n oto.
\v 9 A 30plan otariba ikia 30plan guiviba iti. Egha uan guiviba amangiz…® me nguibar igharazibar gumazibar ikiasa ghue. Ez…® a igharazir adarazir guivir igiaba inigha uan otaribagh an…®ngiz…® me dar iti. Ez…® Ipsan 7plan azenibar Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n ike.
\v 10 Egha an aremez…®, me Betlehem…®n anefa.
\s1 Elon gumazir dapanim…®n oto
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Ipsan aremez…®, Sebulun adarazir gumazir mam Elon, a Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n otogha 10plan azenibar men gari.
\v 12 Ez…® an aremez…®, me Sebulun…®n nguazim…®n, Aijalon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n anefa.
\s1 Apdon gumazir dapanim…®n oto
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Elon aremez…®, Piraton…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim Apdon, a Hilel…®n otarim, a Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n oto.
\v 14 A 40plan otariba ikia igiav otarir 30pla iti. Me zurara donkin 70pla gapiaghira mang…® izegh gami. Ez…® Apdon 8plan azenibar Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n ike.
\v 15 Ez…® an aremez…®, me Efraim…®n nguazim…®n, Piraton…®n anefa. Nguibar kam Amalekian m…®ghs…®ar dozibar iti.
\c 13
\ms1 Samson…®n eghaghanim
\mr (Sapta 13--16)
\s1 Manoan amuim Samson bate
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® Israelia ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh amima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Filistiaba ataghiz…®, me 40plan azenibar me gativagha men gari.
\p 
\v 2 Ez…® Manoa, Dan…®n anabam…®n gumazir mam, a Soran nguibar ekiam…®n iti. An amuim boriba batir puvat…®.
\v 3 Ez…® dughiar mam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel…®n mam iza kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® faragha otir puvat…®. Egh n…® k…®ran oveghang…®n navim asegh otarim bategham.
\v 4 Kamagh…®n, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n wainba ko d…®par onganibar aman mark…®. Egh bizir k…® daman gumazamizibar anogorogheziba, n…® dar aman mark…®. Kar bizir gumazamizibagh ami, me nan damazim…®n m…®zeziba.
\v 5 \x - \xo 13:5 \xt D…®boboniba 6:1-5; 1 Samuel 1:11\x*N…® navim asegh…®va otarim bategham. Egh an dapanir ar…®zim gisan mark…®. A n…®n navim…®n aven itima, God ua bagha a ginaba. Eght…® n…® a bateght…®, a wainba ko d…®par onganibar aman mark…®, egh uaghan God daman gumazibar anogoroghezir dagheba, a dar aman mark…®. Eght…® a ua Filistiaba da Israelia iniam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® amizir kam ghua uan pam Manoan m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir akam akurir mam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel…®n m…®n gara na ko m…®gei. Ez…® k…® bar atiatigha an azarazir puvat…®, a ten gumazim egha a managh ize. A uan ziam…®n gun na m…®kemezir puvat…®.
\v 7 A na m…®g…®a ghaze, k…® navim asegh…®va otarim bategham. Egh wainba ko d…®par onganibar aman kogh…®va uaghan, dagher God daman gumazamizibar anogoroghezibar aman kogham. Bizir kaba, gumazamizibagh amima me nan damazim…®n m…®ze. Eght…® gan otarir nan navim…®n aven ikiamin kam, God ua baghv…®ra a ginabagham, eght…® a kamagh…®ra ik…® mang…® aremegham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® Manoa m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baregha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúO Ekiam, ga uaning, k…® kamagh…®n ifonge, gumazir n…® amadazir kam, n…® uam anemadaght…® a ga bagh iz…®. Eght…® borir g…®n otivamin kam, ga a bagh damuamin biziba a bar dar gun ga m…®k…®mam.‚Äù
\v 9 Ez…® God Manoan m…®g…®r…®g…®am baraghiz…®, Manoan amuim uan azenim…®n aperaghav itima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel iza a bato. Manoa dughiar kam…®n a ko itir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® an amuim bem…®ra uamategha ivegha ghua uan pam batogha an m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® zuam…®ra iz…®! Gumazir faragha iza na batozim, anar…®ra ua iza na bato.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Manoa uan amuim ko uamategha ghua gumazir kam batogha an azara, ‚ÄúN…® gumazir kamra faragha iza nan amuim batoz, o?‚Äù
\p Ez…® gumazim a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúAre, kar k…®rara.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Manoa gumazim…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® nan amuim ko akam ak…®rizir bizir kam guizbang…®ra otoght…®, otarir kam bizir tizibar amuva Akar Gavgavir manabar g…®n mangam?‚Äù
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel kamagh…®n Manoa m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…®n amuim bar derav…®ra m…®g…®r…®g…®ar k…® a m…®kemezibar g…®nt…®gh.
\v 14 A wain…®n ov…®zibar aman mark…®. Egh wain…®n d…®paba ko d…®par onganibar aman mark…®. Egh God daman gumazamizibar anogoroghezir daghebar aman mark…®, bizir kaba gumazamizibagh ami me nan damazim…®n m…®ze. A bar derav…®ra k…® a m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®abar g…®nt…®gh.‚Äù
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Manoa kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa uaning, n…® tong ga ko kagh ik…®t…®ma ga memen igiatam m…®suegh, a isamight…®, n…® damegh mangam.‚Äù
\v 16 Manoa kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel m…®gei.
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ensel kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ik…® gua tuaghamin daghetam ameghan kogham. Gua meme m…®suegh a tus…®, gua Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rizim damu, a tuaght…® a bar isigh.‚Äù
