\p Ez…® 3plan arueba g…®vaz…®, me akar is…®n zuir kam g…®fozir puvat…®ghav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 15 Egha aruer namba 4…®n, me kamagh…®n Samson…®n amuim m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan pam apezeper a gakaghont…®, a uan akar is…®n zuim…®n m…®ngarim…®n gun e m…®kemegh. Puvat…®ght…®, n…® uan adarazi ko, e avim…®n ia daboroght…® ia isigham. Gua en biziba ok…®masa en diaz…®, e kagh ize?‚Äù
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® Samson…®n amuim ghua an guam…®n garava aziava kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® ti na gifongezir puvat…®. Egha akar is…®n zuir kam…®n nan adaraziv kemegha, an m…®ngarim…®n gun na m…®kemezir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p Samson kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n ami? N…® gan, k…® uan amebam ko afeziam m…®kemezir puvat…®. K…® tizim bagh n…® m…®k…®mam?‚Äù
