\v 3 Ez…® Samson atara kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Filistiaba bar me gas…®ghasigh, egh os…®mt…®ziba puvat…®gham. Kar men os…®mt…®zimra.‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® Samson ghua afiar atiar 300plan suigha da inigha dar ipebar uarir fufugha da ike. Egha vaghvagha korir avibar dar ipebagh ike.
\v 5 Egha Samson afiar atiabar ipebar itir korir avibagh apongez…® da isima, ana da ataghiz…®ma, da tintinibar ivemara ghua Filistiabar wit…®n azenibar aven zuima, korir aviba men wit…®n d…®ghoregha ar…®ghiziba ko m…®tivighav itiba sara bar mogh…®ra dar isi. Ez…® wain…®n ikar…®ziba ko oliv…®n temeba uaghan isi.
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Filistiaba kamagh…®n ganigha uarira uari azangs…®si, ‚ÄúTinara bizir kam gami?‚Äù
\p Ez…® gumazir mam kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúSamson a gami. An ivozir afeziam, Timnan nguibam…®n gumazim. A Samson…®n amuim inigha, an namakar a ko an amuim…®n isam…®n dughiam…®n ikezim gan…®ngi.‚Äù Ez…® Filistiabar gumazir dapaniba, Timnan nguibam…®n ghuavanaga Samson…®n amuim ko an afeziam gaboroz…® aning isi.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® Samson kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa arazir kamagh…®n garim gami, a? K…® kamagh…®n akar kam ak…®ram, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n zuam…®ra avughseghan kogham. K…® faragh ia amizir arazir kam ikaragh, egh g…®n avughsam.‚Äù
\v 8 Samson puv me m…®sogha, me ab…®ragha men av…®ribav soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha a g…®n ghua Etam…®n M…®ghs…®ar ekiar mam…®n dag…®ar ak…®riam…®n aven iti.
\s1 Samson Filistiaba ab…®ra
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® Filistiaba g…®n ghua Judabar nguazim…®n averpenibar ingarigha ikia, Lehin nguibam…®n gumazamiziba ko m…®soghasa.
\v 10 Ez…® Judaba kamagh…®n men azangs…®si, ‚ÄúIa bar tizim bagha iza e ko m…®soghasa?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Filistiaba kamagh…®n me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúE Samson…®n suiragh, a inigh mang…® kalabus dar…®ghasa. An e gamizir arazimra, e uaghan kamagh…®ram a damuam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Judabar 3,000plan gumaziba Samson bagha Etam…®n dag…®ar ak…®riam iti nagh…®n ghuaghira kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n fo, Filistiaba e gativagha g…®fa? N…® tizim bagha os…®mt…®zir dafar kam gamigha os…®mt…®zim e gan…®ngi?‚Äù
\p Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúMe na gamizir arazimra k…® a ikarvagha me gami.‚Äù
