\v 13 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE bar guizbang…®ra n…® m…®gei. E n…®n m…®sueght…®, n…® aremeghan kogham. E pura n…® ikegh n…® inigh mang…® Filistiabar agharim dar…®gham.‚Äù Egha me benir gavgavir igiar pumuning inigha an agharimning ikegha, a inigha dag…®ar ak…®riam ategha Filistiaba bagha zui.
