\v 14 Egha me ghua Lehin nguibam…®n otivigha g…®vaz…®ma, Filistiaba a bagha dagarvagha ivemara izi. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Duam Samson giz…®vagha gavgavir ekiam a gan…®ngi. Ez…® benir igiar gavgavir me an agharimning ikezir kaba, mati avim strinbar isiz…® da pura amera d…®ghoraghire.
\v 15 Ez…® a gari donkin mam aremegha ir…®ghav ikia, t…®ghar bar kuram, an an akaguar agharim inigha an suiragha gumazir 1,000pla m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 16 Egha Samson kamagh…®n ighiar mam gami:
