\q2 k…® gumazir av…®ribav soghez…®, me ariaghire.
\q2 Egha k…® men kuabar pozibav k…®niz…®, da mamagh…®ra iti.
\q1 Donkin akaguar agharim…®n,
\q2 k…® gumazir 1,000pla, bar me ag…®fa.‚Äù
