\v 4 Ez…® bizir kam otogha g…®vaz…®ma, Samson Gasan zui. A ghua Sorek…®n danganir zarim…®n amizir mam bato, an ziam Delaila, an an ganigha a bagha bar ifonge.
\v 5 Ez…® Filistian atriviba ghua kamagh…®n Delailan m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Samson apezeperegh, an gavgavim bagh an azaragh, a managh gavgavir ekiar kam isi, eght…® e manmagh…®ra a damight…®, an gavgavim aneteght…®, e aneb…®ragham. N…® an gun en m…®kemeght…® e an suiragh a ikegham. N…® kamagh…®n damight…® e vaghvagh 1,100 silvan dag…®aba is…® n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® Delaila kamagh…®n Samson m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® na m…®k…®m, n…® manmagh…®n gavgavir kam isi? Egh n…® manmagh…®n damight…® gavgavim n…® ateght…® me n…®n suiragh n…® ikegham?‚Äù
