\v 7 Ez…® Samson kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazitam bulmakaun sueba ko dafaribar itir 7plan ag…®rir m…®s…®ngizir puvat…®zir taba inigh na ikeght…®ma, nan gavgavim g…®vaght…®, k…® pura gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 8-9 Ez…® Filistian gumazir dapaniba bulmakaun sueba ko dafaribar itir ag…®rir 7plan m…®s…®ngizir puvat…®ziba inigha iza Delaila gan…®ngi. Ez…® gumazir maba Delaila akui nagh…®n mongeghav iti. Ez…® Delaila Samson…®n suemning ko dafarimning ike. Egha Delaila a gaghura ghaze, ‚ÄúSamson, Filistiaba n…®n suighasa izi!‚Äù Ez…® a d…®kavima bulmakaun ag…®rir kaba, mati strin avir m…®zariam…®n borogh…®n ikia isia d…®ghoraghirezi mogh…®n, d…®ghoraghire. Ez…® Filistiaba an gavgavim…®n m…®ngarim g…®fozir puvat…®ghav…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Delaila kamagh…®n Samson m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® oragh, ga uaning, n…® bar na gifaragha aghums…®zir dafam na gan…®ngi! N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n guizbang…®ra na m…®k…®m, me manmagh…®ra damigh n…®n suiragham?‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® Samson kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGumaziba benir gavgavir bar igiaba inigh na ikeght…® nan gavgavir kam g…®vaght…® k…® pura gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® g…®n Filistiaba iza Delaila akuir danganim…®n modogha itima, Delaila benir gavgavir bar igiar maba inigha an suemning ko agharimning ike. Egha Samson…®n dei, ‚ÄúSamson, Filistiaba n…®n suighasa iz…®!‚Äù Ez…® Samson benir gavgavir bar igiar an agharimning ikezir kaba, tret…®n m…®n dar ghore.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Delaila Samson m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® bar na gifarava aghums…®zir dafam na gan…®di. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n na m…®k…®m, gumaziba bar manmagh…®ra n…® ikegham?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Samson kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan 7plan dapanir ar…®zir g…®zg…®ziba, inigh iniba nuavir masin…®n aven tretba sara initam nuavigh…®va, nan dapanir ar…®zim nir kam…®n aven tretba sara a nuafigh. Egh g…®n d…®konir ruarir tam…®n nir kam is…® b…®rim…®n a gafught…®, a b…®rim…®n porogh gavgafigh. Eght…® k…® ua gavgaviba puvat…®gh pura gumazir igharazibar m…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 14 Ez…® Delaila Samson gamiz…® an akuima, an an 7plan dapanir ar…®zir g…®zg…®ziba, inigha iniba nuavir masin…®n aven, tretba sara inir mam nuavighava, an dapanir ar…®zim inir kam…®n aven tretba sara a nuafi. Egha g…®n d…®konir ruarir mam nir kam sara b…®rim…®n a gafu, ez…® a b…®rim…®n porogha gavgafi. Egha a kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúSamson, n…® ua bagh ganigh, Filistiaba n…®n suighasa izi.‚Äù Ez…® a d…®kavima, d…®konir kam ko nir an dapanir nuavizim…®n ar…®zir g…®zg…®ziba, a bar b…®rim…®n dagh ekuigha d…®kafi.
\p 
\v 15 Ez…® Delaila kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® manmaghsua, na m…®g…®a ghaze, n…® bar na gifonge? N…® bar puv…®ra na gifari. N…® na ko navir vam…®ran itir puvat…®gha guiz…®n akabar na m…®geir puvat…®. Dat…®r…®gh…®n namba 3…®n dughiam, n…® na gifaragha aghums…®zim na gan…®ngi, egha na m…®kemezir puvat…®, n…® manmagh…®ra amigha bar gavgafi.‚Äù
\v 16 Ez…® Delaila dughiabar uab…® m…®k…®masa a gimobava, an azangs…®gha mamagh…®ra iti. Ez…® Samson m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baragha ghua bar iporpore.
\p 
\v 17 Egha bar abuan, a Delaila m…®keme. A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® agh…®rimra iti God na ginabaz…® nan amebam na batezir dughiam…®n, ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, me tong nan dapanir ar…®zibagh isezir puvat…®. Me nan dapanir ar…®zibagh iseght…®, k…® ua gavgaviba puvat…®gh, pura gumazir k…®nim…®n m…®n ikiam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Delaila fo, Samson guizbang…®ra a m…®gei. Egha a Filistiabar atriviba bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúIa uamategh iz…®. A dat…®r…®gh…®n guizbang…®ra uab…®n gun na m…®keme.‚Äù Ez…® Filistiabar gumazir dapaniba, silvan dag…®ar Delaila dan…®ngasa m…®kemeziba inigha izi.
\v 19 Ez…® Delaila Samson gifaraz…®ma Samson an apozim…®n akuava ongani. Ez…® Delaila gumazir mam…®n diaz…®ma a iza Samson dapanir ar…®zir g…®zg…®zir nuavizir 7plan ruariba ap…®ri. Ez…® Delaila arazir kam…®n Samson…®n gavgavim bar aneg…®fa. An gavgavim bar mogh…®ra g…®fa.\f + \fr 16:19 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® Delaila ua kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúSamson, n…® ganigh, Filistiaba n…®n suighasa izi!‚Äù
\p Ez…® Samson osegha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® faragha ami mogh…®n, d…®kavigh mang…® f…®righ…®r…®gham.‚Äù A kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God anetaki.
\v 21 Ez…® Filistiaba an suiragha an damazimning asiaghat…®. Egha me a inigha Gasan ghuegha sen…®n brasbar ingarizim…®n a ike. Egha a gamima a kalabuziar d…®penim…®n aven ikia witba ko raiziaba m…®rm…®ri.
\v 22 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Samson…®n dapanir ar…®zim uam aghui.
\s1 Samson areme
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® dughiar mam…®n Filistiabar atriviba iza uari akuvagha, isar ekiar mam gamua uan asem Dagon bagha ofa gami. Egha me bar akongegha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEn asem en akuraz…®ma e uan apanim Samson…®n suiragha aneb…®ra.‚Äù
\p 
\v 24-25 Egha me g…®n bar akongegha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Samson…®n aku iz…®t…® a uan arazitabar amut…®, e an gan an ingar…®va ak…®, a d…®povasa.‚Äù Ez…® gumaziba ghua kalabus…®n a inigha izi.
\p Ez…® gumazamiziba an ganigha, uan asem…®n ziam fava kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEn asem en akuraz…®ma e uan apanir kam aneb…®ra. Gumazir kam bar en nguazim gas…®ghasigha, en gumazir av…®ribav soghez…® me ariaghire.‚Äù Egha me a isava d…®penim…®n dag…®ar guarir ak…®nimning…®n t…®zim…®n anet…®z…®ma, a tughav ikia arazarazibagh amima, me an ingarava aka a d…®pofi.
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Samson, otarir an dafarim…®n suigha an akuava aruim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® nan akuraght…®ma, k…® d…®penim…®n guarir ak…®nimning…®n suiragh m…®t…®gh, uan ak…®rim is…®va guarir ak…®nimning garoroghasa.‚Äù
\v 27 D…®penir kam gumazamizir bar av…®rim a giz…®fa, ez…® Filistiabar atriviba bar mogh…®ra uaghan me ko iti. Ez…® 3,000plan gumazamiziba d…®penir ekiar kam…®n siriam…®n p…®n ikia beragha Samson…®n garava a d…®povava ati.
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® Samson kamagh…®n diagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, nan Ekiam, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n na g…®n…®ghn…®gh. O God, n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ua gavgavim na dan…®ngigh. Eght…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Filistiaba nan damazimning asiz…® mogh…®ra, k…® me ikaragham.‚Äù
\v 29 Egha Samson dag…®ar d…®penir guarir tong…®ra tughav ikia, gavgavim a gan…®dir ak…®nimning…®n suira. A dafarir guvim…®n guarir ak…®nir mam…®n suiragha, dafarir k…®riam…®n igharazim…®n suira.
\p 
\v 30 Egha a kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúN…® na ateght…® k…® Filistiaba ko aremeka.‚Äù Egha a bar uan gavgaviba sara guarir ak…®nimning adugha zuima d…®penim ir…®. D…®penim d…®p…®righa ira Filistiabar atriviba ko, gumazamizir igharazir an aven itiba sara me gis…®n ira me m…®soghez…®, me bar ariaghire. Ez…® gumazamizir bar av…®rim Samson ko ariaghire, men d…®bobonim, an angam…®ra ikia m…®soghez…® gumazibar d…®bobonim gafira.
\p 
\v 31 Ez…® Samson…®n adarazi g…®n izaghira an kuam ini. Me an kuam inigha ghua Sora ko Estaol…®n nguibar ekiamning…®n t…®zimning…®n, an afeziam Manoa afaz…® nagh…®n anefa. Samson 20plan azenibar Israelian gumazir dapanim…®n ike.
\c 17
\ms1 Benjamin ko Dan…®n // anabamning…®n eghaghaniba
\mr (Sapta 17--21)
\s1 Maika uab…® marvir guabar ziaba fer d…®penir mam iti
\p 
\v 1 Ez…® gumazir mam an ziam Maika, a Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar iti.
\v 2 A dughiar mam…®n uan amebam m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® uan 1,100…®n dag…®ar silvabagh fo, tina da okeme? Ez…® k…® dughiar kam…®n itima, n…® God m…®g…®a ghaze da okemezir gumazim, n…® a gas…®ghas…®kigh. N…® gan, k…® uab…® bizir kam gami. K…® da okemegha, dat…®r…®gh…®n ua n…® gan…®di.‚Äù
\p Ez…® an amebam kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúNan otarim, Ikiav…®ra Itir God deragh n…® damu.‚Äù
\p 
\v 3 Ez…® Maika 1,100plan silvan dag…®aba uamategha da isava uan amebam gan…®ngi. Ez…® an amebam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® silvan dag…®ar kaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God danight…®, dag…®ar kaba nan otarim baghav…®ra ikiam. Egh dag…®ar kaba, ga da is…®va gumazitabar anight…®, me dar marvir guatamning…®n ingaright…®, e aning…®n ziamning fam. Me temer otevitam marvir guatam ak…®righ…®va silvan a nokegh, egh marvir guatam silvan k…®nimra an ingarigh.‚Äù\f + \fr 17:3 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. E uaghan fozir puvat…®, aning manmagh garir nedazim…®n d…®g…®rim silvan kam…®n a gami. Ez…® 18:24…®n akam…®n, Maika nedazimning kamagh…®n aning d…®bori, ‚Äúaser god…®n k…® ingarizimning.‚Äù\f*
\v 4 Egha Maikan amebam 200 silvan dag…®ar an amebam uam a gan…®ngiziba, isa silvan marvir guabar d…®g…®ribagh amir gumazir mam gan…®ngi. Ez…® a marvir guar mam temem…®n anek…®righa silvan bar a noke, egha marvir guar mam silvan k…®nim…®n an ingari. Ez…® amebam aning…®n nedazimning isava Maikan d…®penim…®n aning at…®.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® gumazir kam Maika, a marvir guamning bagha ofa gamir d…®penir dozir mam iti. Egha a ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n korotiar otevir azenan azuir mam…®n ingarigha asebar ifongiam g…®fofoghamin marvir guar dozir mam sara ingari. Egha a uan otarir mam am…®sevez…®ma an ofa gamir d…®penir kam…®n ofa gamir gumazim…®n oto.\f + \fr 17:5 \ft E fozir puvat…®, ‚Äúasebar ifongiam g…®fofoghamin marvir guar dozir mam,‚Äù a ti bar bizir tizimra. N…® Jenesis 31:30 ko 1 Samuel 19:13…®n gan. Hibrun akam…®n bizir kaba me kamagh…®n da d…®bora ghaze, asebar marvir guaba.\f*
\v 6 \x - \xo 17:6 \xt God…®n Araziba 12:8; Gumazir Dapaniba 21:25\x*Dughiar kabar atrivitam Israel…®n itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, gumazamiziba vaghvagha tintinibar uan ifongiabar g…®n ghua pura bizibagh amua iti.
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Livain anabam…®n adarazir gumazir igiar mam, a Judan anabam…®n nguazim…®n ikia, Betlehem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n iti.
\v 8 A Betlehem ategh mang…® nguibar igiatam batogh an ikiasa zui. A ghua Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar, Maikan d…®penim…®n oto.
\v 9 Ez…® Maika an azara, ‚ÄúN…® managh ikegha izi?‚Äù Ez…® Livain gumazir kam kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Betlehem…®n itir Livain anabam…®n gumazir mam, a Judan nguazim…®n itir nguibam. K…® danganir ikiamiba buriagha arui.‚Äù
\p 
\v 10 Ez…® Maika kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® na ko kagh ikiam. N…® na ko ik…® n…®ghn…®ziba na dan…®ng egh uaghan nan ofa gamir gumazim…®n ikiam. Eght…® azenibar zurara k…® 10pla silvan dag…®aba ko korotiaba ko dagheba sara n…® dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\v 11 Kamagh…®n, Livain gumazir igiar kam Maikan m…®g…®r…®g…®am baregha, a ko iti. Egha an an borim…®n m…®n otogha a ko iti.
\v 12 Ez…® Maika ivezim isa Livain gumazir igiar kam gan…®di. Egha a gamiz…® an an ofa gamir gumazim…®n otogha, Maikan d…®penim…®n aven iti.
\p 
\v 13 Ez…® Maika kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúLivain mav dat…®r…®gh…®n nan ofa gamir gumazim…®n otogha iti. Kamagh…®n, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God dat…®r…®gh…®n na danganim…®n aven itir bizibar amight…®, da deragh otivam.‚Äù
\c 18
\s1 Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi nguibar ekiar igiam ini
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n Israelia atriviba puvat…®. Dan…®n anabam fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, me Israelian anababar tong…®n, nguazir tam inizir puvat…®ghav…®ra iti, kamagh…®n, Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi nguazir tam batogh an ikiasa da buri.
\v 2 Ez…® Dan…®n anabam…®n adarasi, gumazir bar gavgavir 5pla am…®sevez…®, me Sora ko Estaol…®n nguibar ekiamning…®n iti. Me Dan…®n anababar 5plan gumazir kaba am…®sevegha, me amadaz…®ma, me ghua moga nguazim…®n gara a getiagha arui. Me kamagh…®n gumazir kabav gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® nguazir kam bar deraghv…®ram a getiraru.‚Äù Ez…® gumazir 5plan kaba ghua Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar Maikan d…®penim…®n otogha, d…®magarir vam…®ran a koma akui.
\p 
\v 3 Me ghua Maikan d…®penim…®n aven ikia orazima, Livain gumazir kam m…®gei. Ez…® me an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba baregha fo, kar Judabar nguazim…®n gumazim, ez…® me an azara, ‚ÄúN…® bizir tizim gamua kagh iti? Tinara n…® inigha kagh ize?‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® a kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúMaika uab…® na m…®kemez…®, k…® kagh iti. A na givezima k…® an ofa gamir gumazim…®n otogha kagh iti.‚Äù
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® me kamagh…®n Livain gumazir kam m…®gei, ‚ÄúE uari, n…® e bagh God ko m…®k…®m. N…® e bagh God…®n azangs…®gh, en darorir kam deragham, o puvat…®gham?‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amuan mark…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian gan ian darorim geghuvam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 7 Ez…® 5plan gumazir kaba nguibar kam ategha ghua Lais…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto. Me ghua Lais…®n nguibam…®n itir gumazamizibar garima, men dabirabim Saidon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamizibar m…®n dera. Me bar n…®m…®ram apiaghav ikia gumazir igharazibar atari puvat…®. Me ghaze, m…®dorozitam me batoghan kogham. Atrivitam o gumazir dapanitam aghums…®zir arazitam…®n me gamizir puvat…®. Me Saidon…®n nguibam…®n saghon ikia, egha dag…®aba bagha biziba igharaz darazi dama, ada amadir puvat…®.\f + \fr 18:7 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 8 Ez…® 5pla gumazir kaba uamategha ghua Sora ko Estaol…®n otoz…®, men adarazi men azara, ‚ÄúIa manmagh…®ra garir bizibar gani?‚Äù
\p 
\v 9 Ez…® 5plan gumazir kaba kamagh…®n me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa zuam…®ra iz…® e mang…®va, nguibar ekiar kam korogh me m…®sogham. E men nguzim…®n garima, a bar dera. Ia suighsuighan mark…®, e mang…® me m…®sogh men nguazim iniam.
\v 10 Ia danganir kam…®n mang…® gant…®, nguazir av…®riba ikiam. Ia gant…® bizir aghuir av…®riba an ikiam. Egh ia uaghan gant…®, me m…®soghs…® n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. Ia oragh, God nguazir kam e dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 11 Kamagh…®n, Dan…®n adarazir 600plan gumaziba m…®dorozir biziba inigha, m…®soghasa Sora ko Estaol ategha zui.
\v 12 Me ghua Kiriat Jearim…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n Judan nguazim…®n averpenibar ingarigha iti. Kamagh…®n danganir kam me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúDan…®n Averpenibar Ingarizir Danganim.‚Äù Danganir kam Kiriat Jearim…®n aruem uaghiri nagh…®n iti, ez…® me dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®ra a d…®bora mamagh…®ra iti.
\p 
\v 13 Me danganir kam ategha ghua Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar Maikan d…®penim…®n oto.
\v 14 Ez…® 5plan gumazir ghua Lais…®n nguazim moga an ganiziba, kamagh…®n uan adaraziv gei, ‚ÄúIa kamagh…®n fo, d…®penir kabar aven, ofa gamir gumazibar korotiar mam ko, asebar ifongiam g…®fofoghamin marvir guar dozir maba ko, marvir guar me temem…®n d…®k…®righa silvan noghezir mam ko, marvir guar me silvan k…®nim…®n ingarizir mam, da iti. Ez…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n manmagh…®n damuam?‚Äù
\v 15 Ez…® me tuavim ategha Maikan d…®penim iti nagh…®n Livain gumazir igiam itir d…®penim…®n otogha, egha dughiam a gan…®ngi.
\v 16 Me d…®penim…®n aven itir dughiam…®n, Dan…®n m…®dorozir gumazir 600pla uan m…®dorozir bizibar suigha, Maikan d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n itiar akam…®n m…®tivighav iti.
\v 17 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir kam, 600plan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko d…®vazim…®n itiar akam…®n itir dughiam…®n, gumazir 5plan moga gariba, me aseba fer biziba iniasa d…®penim…®n aven ghue. Me ghua ofa gamir gumazibar korotiam ko, God…®n ifongiam g…®fofoghamin marvir guar doziba ko, marvir guar me temem…®n d…®k…®righa silvan noghezim ko, marvir guar me silvan k…®nim…®n ingarizim, me bar ada ok…®masa.
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim garima, gumazir kaba Maikan d…®penim…®n aven ghuegha, ofa gamir gumazibar korotiam ko, God…®n ifongiam g…®fofoghamin marvir guar doziba ko, marvir guar me temem…®n d…®k…®righa silvan noghezim ko, marvir guar me silvan k…®nim…®n ingarizim, me da okei. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúIa tizim gami?‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® me kamagh…®n a m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® uan akam dukuagh n…®m…®ra ik…®. N…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar tam damuan mark…®. N…® uaghan e ko iz…®va en ofa gamir gumazim…®n otogh, egh uaghan n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba e dan…®ngamin gumazim…®n ikiam. N…® ti d…®penir vam…®ra itir gumazim bagh ofa gamir gumazim…®n ikiam? Ingangarir kam, a pura bizim. N…® e ko iz…®va Israelian anabar ekiar tam…®n ofa gamir gumazim…®n ikiam, kar ingangarir bar ekiam, a Maikan ingangarir muziarim bar a gafira.‚Äù
\v 20 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim kamagh…®n oregha navir am…®rizim inigha, ofa gamir gumazibar korotiam ko, God…®n ifongiam g…®fofoghamin marvir guar doziba ko, silvan marvir guamning inigha, men g…®n zui.
\p 
\v 21 Egha me nguibar kam ategha zui. Men boriba ko men bulmakauba ko men biziba faragha zui.
\v 22 Me Maikan d…®penim ategha mong saghuiam me gat…®gha zuima, Maika uan d…®penim…®n borogh…®n itir darazir diagha, me Dan…®n adaraziv soghasa men g…®n zui. Egha me men g…®n ghua me bato.
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® Maika ko m…®soghasa zui darasi, Dan…®n adarazir dei, ez…® Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi ragha Maikan azara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n ami? N…® tizim bagha av…®rir dafar kam ko izi?‚Äù
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® Maika kamagh…®n me ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIa tizim bagha kamagh…®n nan azangs…®si, n…® bar bizir tizim baka? Ia tizim bagha nan ofa gamir gumazim ko nan marvir guar k…® ingarizimning inighava ari? Nan bizitam itir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 25 Ez…® Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi kamagh…®n a ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®ribar e damuan mark…®. Gumazir kaba ua n…®n atar n…® m…®suegh, egh n…®n amuiroghboriba sara m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghiregham.‚Äù
\v 26 Egha Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi kamagh…®n m…®kemegha g…®vagha ghue. Ez…® Maika gumazir kabar garima me bar gavgaviz…®, a me m…®soghan ibura, kamagh…®n, a uamategha uan nguibam…®n ghu.
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi Maika ingarizir biziba ko, an ofa gamir gumazim sara inigha Lais…®n ghu. Ez…® Lais…®n gumazamiziba bar derav…®ra iti. Egha me tong m…®soghasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n, Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghirez…®, me men nguibar ekiam gaboroz…® a isi.
\v 28 Saidon…®n nguibar ekiam bar men saghon iti, kamagh…®n men akurvaghamin gumaziba puvat…®, me uaghan gumazir igharaziba ko biziba uari gan…®ga uari ikarvazir puvat…®. Nguibar kam Betrehop…®n nguibam…®n borogh…®n danganir zarim…®n iti. Ez…® Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi ua nguibar ekiar kam…®n ingarigha an iti.
\v 29 Egha me nguibar kam kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúDan.‚Äù Me uan inazir afeziabar ziam Dan inigha a gat…®, a Jekop…®n otarim, me an ziam isava nguibar ekiar kam gat…®. Me fom…®ra kamagh…®n a d…®bori, ‚ÄúLais.‚Äù
\v 30 Ez…® Dan…®n anabam…®n adarasi, marvir guar me inigha izezim asaragha, an ziam fe. Ez…® Moses…®n otarim Gersom, an ovavir borir mam Jonatan, a Dan…®n adarazi bagha ofa gamir gumazim…®n ingangarim gami. Ez…® an otariba ko an ovavir boriba uaghan ofa gamir ingangarim gamua ghuav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, men apaniba iza bar Israelian suigha ghua, kantrin igharazim…®n kalabus gat…®.\f + \fr 18:30 \ft Akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ti kamagh…®n ghu, dughiar kam…®n, Jonatan uan adarazi ko ofa gamir ingangarim gamima, Asirian adarazi Israel…®n gumazamizir av…®riba inigha ghua, uan kantrin aven kalabus gat…®. Dan…®n anabam…®n adarazi Lais…®n nguibam inigha g…®fa. Ez…® 400plan azenibar g…®n bizir kam oto. N…® 2 Atriviba 15:29…®n gan.\f*
\v 31 God…®n Purirpenim Silon itir dughiam…®n, Dan…®n anabam…®n adarasi, Maika d…®k…®r…®zir marvir guar kam…®n ziam fa mamagh…®ra iti.
\c 19
\s1 Livain gumazir mam uan amuim ko dughiar kuram bato
\p 
\v 1 Dughiar kam…®n Israelia atriviba puvat…®. Ez…® Livain mav Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar iti. A Betlehem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n Judan amizir mam inigha, uan amuir ekiam g…®furagha an ti.
\v 2 Ez…® an amuir dozir kam, bizir mam bagh an atara, uamategha ara ghua uan afeziam…®n d…®penim…®n ghugha itima, 4plan iak…®niba g…®fa.
\v 3 Ez…® g…®n, an pam an g…®n ghua a ko m…®g…®r…®g…®am ak…®righ, a inigh izasa zui. A ingangarir gumazir vam…®ra ko donkin pumuning inigha zui. Aning ghua otoz…®ma, amizim uan pam inigha uan afeziam…®n d…®penim…®n aven ghu. Ez…® an amuim…®n afeziam an ganigha bar akonge.
\v 4 Ez…® amizim…®n afeziam, uan amerer otarim bagha gavgavigha ghaze, an a ko ikiam. Ez…® gumazim 3plan dughiabar me ko ikia, apava d…®paba api.
\p 
\v 5 Ez…® namba 4…®n dughiam…®n, Livain gumazir kam bar d…®mangara d…®kavigha mangasa uan bizibar k…®ri. Ez…® an amuim…®n afeziam kamagh…®n uan amerem m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® daghetamra amegh, gavgavim uan navim dan…®ngigh, egh g…®n mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 6 Ez…® aning uam aperagha apa d…®paba api. Ez…® guivim…®n afeziam ua kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® kamaghsua, n…® ua ghuariar d…®magarir kam…®n ik…®va e bar akongegh mang…® am…®nim tiraght…® gua mang…®.‚Äù
\v 7 Ez…® a d…®kavigh mangasa amima, an amerem ikiasa bar gavgafi. Ez…® a d…®magarir mam…®n ua me ko iti.
\p 
\v 8 Dughiar namba 5…®n bar m…®zaraghara, Livain gumazir kam d…®kavigh mangasa. Ez…® an ivozim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúGa uaning, n…® ikegh daghetam ramegh. Aruem tong am…®raght…®, n…® mangam.‚Äù Ez…® gumazimning uaghara ikiava api.
\p 
\v 9 Egha gumazir kam uan amuir dozim ko ingangarir gumazim, me mangasa amima, amuim…®n afeziam kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gan, aruem bar iraghu. Ia ua d…®magarir kam…®n ikegh, am…®nim k…®ran oveghang…®n p…®ram. Ia ua ik…® bar akongegh. Egh ia gurum…®n d…®mangara d…®kavigh bar mang…® uan nguibamram otogh.‚Äù
\v 10 Ez…® Livain gumazir kam ua d…®magarir tam…®n ikian aghua. Egha a uan amuir dozim ko d…®kavigha zui. Aning uan donkining…®n ak…®rimning…®n itir satelning gaperagha zui.
\p 
\v 11 Ez…® aruem bar uaghirima aning ghua Jebus…®n nguibar ekiam…®n oto, kar Jerusalem…®n ziar igharazim. Ez…® ingangarir gumazim kamagh…®n uan gumazir aruam m…®gei, ‚ÄúE nguibar ekiar kam…®n aven mang…® kagh dakuam.‚Äù
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® ingangarir gumazir kam…®n gumazir aruam ghaze, ‚ÄúPuvat…®, e kagh dakuan kogham, kar Israelian gumazamizibar nguibar ekiam puvat…®. E mang…® Gibean nguibar ekiam…®n dakuam.
\v 13 N…® iz…® e mangam, e tong s…®vagh mang…® Gibea o Raman nguibar ekiam…®n dakuam.‚Äù
\v 14 Egha me Jebus gitagha zui. Ez…® aruem bar uaghirima, me ghua Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazir nguazim…®n, Gibean nguibam…®n borogh…®n otifi.
\v 15 Egha me ghua tuavir ekiam ategha ghuava nguibar ekiam…®n aven ghue, egha dakuamin danganiba bagha gara danganir gumazamiziba uari akuvim…®n apiaghav iti. Ez…® gumazir me batogh, me inigh uan d…®penim…®n mang…® dakuamin tam, otozir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 16 Ez…® me apiagha ikiav…®ra itima, gumazir aser mam izi. A uan azenibar ghua ingarigha uamategha izi. Gumazir aser kam Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar itir gumazim, egha a iza Gibean iti. Gibean itir adarasi, me Benjamin…®n adarasi.
\v 17 Ez…® gumazir aser kam iza garima, Livain gumazir kam, uan amuir dozim ko uan ingangarir gumazim, me gumazamiziba uari akuva itir danganim…®n apiaghav iti. Ez…® gumazir aser kam men azara, ‚ÄúIa managh ikegha ize? Egha ia managh mangasa?‚Äù
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Livain gumazir kam kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE Judan nguazim…®n, Betlehem…®n nguibam…®n ikegha izi. Egha e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n mangasa. Ez…® en nguibam a Efraim…®n m…®ghs…®ar dozibar tong…®n iti, ez…® e mang…® an dakuasa. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, e inigh d…®penim…®n mangamin gumaziba puvat…®.
\v 19 E pura ian ingangarir gumaziba, e dagheba ko biziba bar iti. Donkining…®n dagheba iti. K…® uan amuim ko nan ingangarir gumazim, en bretba ko wainba iti. E bizitam…®n otevezir puvat…®. E dakuamin danganiba buri.‚Äù
\p 
\v 20 Ez…® gumazir aser kam kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúA dera, ia nan d…®penim…®n iz…®. K…® bizibar ian akurvagham. Ia danganir gumazamiziba uari akuva itir kam d…®mangan an ikian kogham.‚Äù
\v 21 Egha a me inigha uan d…®penim…®n ghugha, dagheba isa donkining gan…®ngi. A d…®pam inigha me gan…®ngiz…®ma, me uan dagariba ruegha, g…®n dagheba ko d…®paba api.
\p 
\v 22 \x - \xo 19:22-24 \xt Jenesis 19:5-8\x*Me apava bar akongegha itima, nguibar ekiar kam…®n gumazir arazir kurabagh amir maba izava d…®penim okarigha g…®fa. Egha tiam m…®sogha, d…®penir kam…®n ghuavim m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir n…® ko kagh itim, anemadaght…® an azenan iz…®. E arazir kurabar a damuasa.‚Äù
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® gumazir aser kam azenan ghua kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúPuvat…®. Nan namakam, ia kamagh…®n a damuan kogham. Gumazir kam nan d…®penim…®n izegha na ko iti. Ia arazir kurar kam…®n a damuan kogham.
\v 24 Ia oragh, nan guivir igiar gumazitam ko akuizir puvat…®zim ko gumazir kam…®n amuir dozim iti. K…® aning inigh iz…® ian agharim dar…®gham, eght…® ia damuasa ifongezir arazim ia damus…®, aning ko a damu. Ez…® gumazir kamning ia arazir kurar kam…®n aning damuan kogham.‚Äù
\v 25 Ez…® gumazir kaba gumazir aser kam bar a batoke. Ez…® Livain gumazir kam uan amuir dozim batuegha a isava me gan…®ngi. Ez…® me a inigha arazir kurabar a gamuava tintinibar a gamua ghuavti am…®nim tira. Egha me g…®n anetaghiz…® a zui.
\v 26 Ez…® amizim iza an pam akui nagh…®n, gumazir aser kam…®n d…®penir tiar akam…®n ir…®ghav iti. Egha ir…®ghav ikia ghua am…®nim tiraz…® aruem anadi.
\p 
\v 27 Ez…® am…®nim tiraz…® an pam d…®kavigh mangasa tiam tui. A tiam kuigha garima an amuir dozim ir…®ghav iti. A uan dafarimning tiar akam…®n suighasava amuava avenge.
\v 28 Ez…® Livain gumazir kam kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® d…®kavigh, ga mangam.‚Äù Ez…® amizim tong a m…®geir puvat…®. Ez…® a fo an aremegha g…®fa, ez…® a magh…®ram an kuam isa donki gis…®n anet…®gha a inigha uan nguibam…®n zui.
\v 29 \x - \xo 19:29 \xt 1 Samuel 11:7\x*A ghua nguibam…®n otogha d…®penim…®n aven ghua afuar mam ini. Egha amuir dozim…®n kuam 12plan akuabar aneghore. Egha vaghvagha Israelian 12plan anababa bagha da amangi.
\p 
\v 30 Ez…® gumaziba bar bizir kam…®n ganigha kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúKar arazir bar kuram! E Israelia Isip ategha azenan izezir dughiam…®n iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, bizir kamagh…®n garir tam otoz…® en ganizir puvat…®. Ia bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh uariv k…®m. E manmagh…®ra damuam?‚Äù
\c 20
\s1 Israelia Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko m…®soghasa
\p 
\v 1 Egha Israelia bar Gibean gumaziba amizir arazir kuram…®n akam baregha izava, Mispan nguibar ekiam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Damazim…®n bar mogh…®ra uari akufa. Me not…®n amadaghan Dan…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghua saut…®n amadaghan itir Berseban nguibar ekiam…®n gumaziba ko, Gileat…®n nguazim…®n itir gumaziba uaghan, uan nguibaba ategha iza bar mogh…®ra uari akufa.
\v 2 Ez…® Israelian anababa vaghvagha dar gumazir dapaniba bar mogh…®ra God…®n gumazamizibar iv…®riar ekiam bagha ize. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazibar d…®bobonim 400,000pla uaghan iti, kar m…®dorozir sababar m…®sozir gumaziba.
\v 3 Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi kamagh…®n oraki, Israelian marazi ghua Mispan uari akufa.
\p Ez…® Israelia kamagh…®n Livain gumazir kam…®n azara, ‚ÄúN…® deragh e m…®k…®m, bizir kam manmagh…®n oto?‚Äù
\p 
\v 4 Ez…® amizir me arazir kurabar a gamizim…®n pam, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® uan amuir dozim ko iza Gibean nguibar ekiam…®n Benjamin…®n adarazir nguazim…®n otoz…®, am…®nim p…®riz…®, ga d…®magarim kagh dakuasa danganiba buria iti.
\v 5 Ez…® d…®magarir kam…®n Gibean gumazir aruaba iza d…®penir ga itim okarigha na m…®sueght…® k…® aremeghasa. Egha me na ategha nan amuir dozim inigha arazir bar kurabar a gamua ghuav iti, an areme.
\v 6 Gumazir kaba arazir bar kuram Israelia en tong…®n a gami, kamagh…®n, k…® an kuam inigha iza, aneghoregha an akuaba isa bar Israelian adarazi bagha da amangi.
\v 7 Ez…® ia dat…®r…®gh…®n kagh uari akuvagha itir Israelia, ia derav…®ra n…®ghnigh m…®g…®r…®g…®a tam damu. E manmagh me amizir arazir kam ikarvagham?‚Äù
\p 
\v 8 Ez…® gumaziba bar mogh…®ra d…®kavigha navir vam…®ra ikia kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúEn tav uamategh uan purirpenm…®n mangan kogham. Egh tav uamategh d…®penim…®n mangan kogham.
\v 9-10 Egh e Gibean adarazi kamagh…®n me damuam! E satu gikararang, m…®dorozir gumazibagh inamight…® me arazir kam bagh me m…®sogh me ikaragham. Israelian anababa vaghvagh dar 100plan gumazibar tong…®n 10plan gumaziba am…®s…®vam, egh 1,000plan gumazibar tong…®n 100plan gumaziba am…®s…®vam, egh 10,000plan gumazibar tong…®n 1,000plan gumaziba am…®s…®vam. Gumazir kaba mang…®, Israelia gamizir arazir bar kurar kam ikarvagh…®va, Gibeania ko m…®soghamin m…®dorozir gumaziba bagh dagheba ateram. Me mang…® Geban nguibam…®n ikiam.‚Äù\f + \fr 20:9-10 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Geban nguibam Gibean nguibam…®n borogh…®n iti.\f*
\v 11 Ez…® Israelia bar mogh…®ra uari akuvagha mati anabar vam…®ram otogha, Gibeania ko m…®soghamin n…®ghn…®zir bar vam…®ran iti.
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Israelian adarasi, Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adaraziv k…®masa kamagh…®n gumaziba amadagha me m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…®, arazir bar kurar kam ian tong…®n oto?
\v 13 Ia dat…®r…®gh…®ra Gibean gumazir kurar kaba inigh iz…®t…®, e me m…®sueght…® me ar…®ghiregh arazir kurar kam Israel…®n aven bar aneg…®vagham.‚Äù Ez…® puvat…®, Benjaminia Israelian gumazir igharazibar akaba barazir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 14 Egha Benjamin anabam…®n adarazi bar mogh…®ra uan nguibar ekiaba ategha iza Gibean uari akufa, egha Israelia ko m…®soghasa.
\v 15-16 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi uan 26,000plan gumazir m…®dorozir sababar m…®soziba uan nguibar ekiabar aven bar me ini. Ez…® Gibeania, uarir tong…®n 700plan gumazir agharir k…®riabar m…®soziba ini. Me bar derav…®ra dag…®aba isava katapel gar…®ghava asi. Me asir dag…®atam pura zuir puvat…®, me vaghvagh bar derav…®ra ia gasegham.
\v 17 Ez…® Israelian adarasi, uan 400,000plan gumazir m…®soziba akufa, me m…®dorozir sababar m…®sogha bar fo. Egha me Benjamin…®n adarazir gumazibar d…®bobonir kam, me a medir puvat…®.
\s1 Israelia Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko m…®sosi
\p 
\v 18 Ez…® Israelia Betel…®n nguibam…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n ghuegha, kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azai, ‚ÄúEn adarazir te faragh mang…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko m…®sogham.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúJudan anabam…®n adarazi faragh mang…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 19 Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar m…®zaraghara d…®kavigha ghua Gibean nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n uari akufa.
\v 20 Me mang…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko m…®soghasa uari ak…®ra uari isava danganibar uari ar…®si.
\v 21 Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi Gibean nguibar ekiam ategha azenan iza m…®dorozim foregha, aruer vam…®ran Israelian gumazir 22,000pla aghorez…® me ariaghire.
\v 22-23 Ez…® Israelia uamategha ofa gamir dakozim…®n ghuegha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n guam…®n azia ikia ghuavti, aruem g…®fa. Me kamagh…®n an azai, ‚ÄúE ua uan aveghbuaba, Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko m…®sogham, o markiam?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa uamategh mang…® me ko m…®sogh.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Israelia uamategha gavgavim uarigh anigha, am…®mzaraghan uamategha ghua Gibean, me faragha m…®dorozir gumaziba danganibar me ar…®ghiz…® nagh…®n ua me ar…®si.
\v 24 Ez…® Israelia am…®mzaraghan uamategha ghua Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko uariv sosi.
\v 25 Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ua Gibean nguibar ekiam ategha azenan iza Israelia ko m…®sogha, dughiar kam…®n me men m…®dorozir gumazir 18,000pla m…®dorozir sababar me aghorez…® me ariaghire.
\p 
\v 26 Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba bar mogh…®ra uamategha Betel…®n ghuegha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n apiagha azia ikia ghuavti aruem iraghu. Me daghetam ko d…®patam amezir puvat…®. Egha me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ofan bar isi m…®gh…®ramiba ko, God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofabagh ami.
\v 27-28 (Finias, a Eleasar…®n ovavir borim, ez…® Eleasar an Aron…®n otarim. Dughiar kam…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam Betel…®n nguibam…®n itima, Finias an gara God bagha ofabagh ami.)
\p Ez…® Israelia kamagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azai, ‚ÄúE uamategh mang…® uan aveghbuaba Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko m…®sogham, o e me ategham?‚Äù
\p Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…®. K…® gurumzaraghan me is…® ian agharim dar…®gham.‚Äù
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® Israelia m…®dorozir gumaziba amadaz…®ma, me ghua Gibean nguibar ekiam okarigha mongegha iti.
\v 30 Ez…® aruer pumuning g…®vaz…®ma am…®mzaraghan Israelia Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko m…®soghasa zui. Me faragha Gibean nguibar ekiam…®n amiz…® mogh…®ra, m…®dorozir gumaziba isa me ar…®si.
\v 31 Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi m…®soghasa izima, Israelia me gekuigha mong s…®vagha zuima, me nguibar ekiam…®n azenan ghue. Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi faragha amiz…® mogh…®n, tuavir ekiabar Israelia m…®sosi. Me Betel…®n zuir tuavim, ko Gibean zuir tuavim, ko tintinibar nguibaba ko azenibar, puv…®ra me m…®sogha, Israelian 30plan gumazibav soke.
\v 32 Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ‚ÄúE faragha me m…®sogha me ab…®raz…® mogh…®n, dat…®r…®gh…®n me e me gafiragha g…®fa.‚Äù
\p Ez…® Israelia kamagh…®n uarira uariv gei, ‚ÄúE me gifar…®va ar…® nguibar ekiam ategh ar…® tuavir ekiam…®n mangam.‚Äù
\v 33-34 Egha Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rir dafam, dat…®r…®gh…®n bar mogh…®ra uamategha ghua Baltamar…®n nguibam…®n uari akufa. Ez…® men marazi ghua aruem uaghiri nagh…®n Geban nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n monge. Gumazir kaba, me faragha Israelian gumazibar tong…®n, men m…®dorozir gumazir bar aghuir kabav sefe, men d…®bobonim 10,000…®n tu. Me mongeghav ikegha magh…®ra otivigha, bar m…®dorozir gavgavim Gibeania gami. Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, dat…®r…®gh…®n kar me g…®vaghamin dughiam, otogha g…®fa.
\v 35 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian akuraz…®ma, me m…®dorozim…®n Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ab…®ra. Ez…® aruer kamra Israelia Benjamin…®n adarazir m…®dorozir gumazir 25,100pla m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 36 Egha Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi kamagh…®n fo, Israelia m…®dorozim…®n me ab…®ragham.
\s1 Israelia m…®dorozim…®n Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ab…®ragha bar me ag…®fa
\p Israelia faragha uan m…®dorozir gumazir mabav kemez…® me Gibean nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n monge. Ez…® Israelian gumazir igharaziba fo, men marazi mongeghav…®ra iti. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n me gifara ara zuima, Benjamin…®n adarazi men g…®nt…®si. Guizbang…®ra, me Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazigh gifarava ara me gekuigha bar ghua nguibar ekiam ataki.
\v 37 Ez…® gumazir mongez…® kaba zuam…®ram otivigha Gibean nguibar ekiam…®n aven ghua gumazamizir aven itiba bar me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire.
\v 38 M…®dorozir gumazir ara zuir kaba, me faragha m…®dorozir gumazir mongeziba koma kamagh…®n akam m…®sogha ghaze, ia avir m…®turir ekiam…®n gant…®, a nguibar ekiar kam gis…®n mavanangt…®,
