\v 41 Ez…® Israelian gumazir av…®rir dafam uamategha izi. Ez…® Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi garima Israelia uamategha izima me bar atiatingiz…®, men gavgaviba bar g…®fa. Egha me kamagh…®n fo me dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar bar kuram me batogham.
\v 42 Kamagh…®n, me Israelian ara tuavir ghua gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n zuim…®n ghue. Me aramin tuaviba puvat…®. Me ghua Israelian adarazi batifi. Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir okoruar pumuning iza Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi batogha bar me m…®soaghar…®ghiz…® me ariaghire.\f + \fr 20:42 \ft Hibrun akam deragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f*
\v 43 Israelia Menuhan nguibam…®n Benjamin…®n adarazir ag…®nt…®gha ghua Gibean nguibam…®n vong…®n amadaghan aruem anadi nagh…®n tu. Egha me puv…®ra me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 44 Ez…® me aruer kam…®n Benjamin…®n adarazir 18,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir bar gavgavibav soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 45 Ez…® Benjamin…®n adarazir marazi uamategha arava gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n itir Rimon…®n Dag…®ar Dafam bagha zui. Ez…® Israelia men ag…®nt…®gha ghua tuavim…®n men gumazir 5,000pla m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Israelia men g…®nt…®gha ghuav…®ra ikia Gidom…®n nguibam…®n tu. Egha ua 2,000plan gumazibav soghez…® me ariaghire.
\v 46 Ez…® aruer kamra, ariaghirezir gumaziba bar, men d…®bobonim 25,000…®n tu. Kar m…®dorozir gumazir bar gavgavibara.
\v 47 Ez…® men 600plan gumaziba uamategha ara ghua gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n, Rimon…®n Dag…®ar Dafam iti nagh…®n ghue. Egha 4plan iak…®nibar danganir kam…®n iti.
\v 48 Ez…® Israelia uamategha ghua men gumazamiziba ko men as…®ziba bar dav soghez…®, da ariaghire. Egha bizir tizir me uan damazibar gariba sara bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki. Egha Benjamin…®n adarazir nguibar ikiav…®ra itir varazira, me bar dagh apongez…® da bar isi.
\c 21
\s1 Israelia amizir Benjamin…®n gumazibar ikiamiba bagha n…®ghn…®si
\p 
\v 1 Israelia Mispan nguibar ekiam…®n itir dughiam…®n, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n akam ak…®righa ghaze, ‚ÄúBenjamin…®n anabam…®n gumazitam, en guivitam…®n ikian kogham.‚Äù
\v 2 M…®dorozim g…®vaz…®ma, Israelia bar mogh…®ra ghua Betel…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghuegha, God…®n damazim…®n apiagha, bar puv…®ram azia mamagh…®ra ikia ghuavti aruem iraghu.
