\v 3 Me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® Israelian God. N…® tizim bagha bizir kam gamiz…®, an oto? Manmagh…®n amiz…®, en anabar mam k…®ran oveghang…®n bar g…®vagham?‚Äù
