\v 4 Egha am…®mzaraghan bar d…®mangara, Israelia d…®kavigha nguibar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofa damuasa dakozir mam…®n ingari. Egha bar isi m…®gh…®ramin ofaba ko, gumazamiziba God ko navir vam…®ra ikiamin ofaba, isa an damazim…®n dagh ami.
\v 5 Egha me kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIsraelian adarazir terara Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ghuzir puvat…®?‚Äù Me faragha m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavim gamigha ghaze, gumazitam Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh Mispan izeghan koght…®, me a m…®sueght…® an aremegham.
