\v 16 Ez…® Israelian gumazir dapaniba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBenjamin…®n anabam…®n amiziba bar ariaghire. Ez…® e manmagh…®n men gumazir ariaghirezir puvat…®zir varazira bagh amizitaba iniam?
\v 17 Me amuiba puvat…®gh borir taba bateghan koght…®, en anabar kam bar kuavaremegham. Men ikiav…®ra itir varazira, amizitaba inigh dar ik…®t…® me boriba bat…®t…®, men anabar kam kuvaremeghan kogham.
\v 18 Guizbang…®ra, e men gumazitam ateght…®, a en guivitam…®n ikian kogham. E Israelia faragha akar gavgavim ak…®righa ghaze, ‚ÄòGumazitam uan guivim is…®va Benjamin…®n anabam…®n gumazitam danigh, an aremegham.‚Äô Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e uan guivitam men teght…®, men an ikian kogham.‚Äù
